Zhang Guangjun was appointed vice governor of Guangdong province .
the fifth meeting of the standing committee of the 13 th Guangdong provincial people 's congress held its second plenary session in Guangzhou on 30 august .
after a vote , the meeting decided to appoint Zhang guangjun as vice governor of the Guangdong provincial people 's government .
before that , Zhang guangjun was deputy secretary of the party committee of the chinese academy of engineering physics .
curriculum vitae of comrade Zhang guangjun : Zhang guangjun , male , han nationality , born in february 1968 , of Chongqing nationality , joined the party in april 1994 , took part in work in july 1991 , graduated from Harbin industrial university 's radio engineering department in electronics and measuring technology , received a university degree , senior engineer , and enjoyed special subsidies from the state council government .
he is currently vice governor and member of the party group of the Guangdong provincial government .
1987 @-@ 1991 Studies in Electronics and Measurement Technology , Department of Radio Engineering , Harbin University of Technology
1991 @-@ 1998 Technician , Deputy Director , Secretary and Deputy Director , General Engineering Institute , Chinese Academy of Engineering Physics
1998 @-@ 2002 Deputy Director of the General Engineering Institute of the Chinese Academy of Engineering Physics and Deputy Secretary of the Party Committee ( during which : 1999.05 @-@ 2000.12 also served as Secretary of the Disciplinary Commission of the Institute , 2001.09 @-@ 2001.12 )
2002 @-@ 2002 Party Secretary and Deputy Director , Institute of General Engineering , Chinese Academy of Engineering Physics ( In between : 2002.03 @-@ 2004.05 Advance Course in Management Science and Engineering , Fudan University School of Management )
2002 @-@ 2009 Director of the Political Department of the Chinese Academy of Engineering Physics , Director of the Party Committee &apos;s Office and Vice @-@ President of the Party School ( In between : 2005.09 @-@ 2006.01 Training Course for Young and Middle @-@ aged Cadres of the Central Party School )
2009 @-@ 2014 Director , Major Management Office , Chinese Academy of Engineering Physics ( during which : 2011.09 @-@ 2012.01 Training Course for Young and Middle @-@ aged Cadres , Central Party School )
2014 @-@ 2015 Assistant to the President of the Chinese Academy of Engineering Physics and Head of the Major Engineering Management Office
2015 @-@ 2018 Deputy Secretary of the Party Committee , Chinese Academy of Engineering Physics
September 2018 Vice Governor and member of the Party Group of Guangdong Provincial Government
according to british media , us navy deputy director of operations , general William Moran , said : even as the us navy is reinvigorating its strength to deal with russia , which is increasingly worrying on both sides of the atlantic , the united states continues to make the focus of its navy on expanding the asia - pacific region to include the Indian ocean , asia , and the pacific region .
the united states listed china and russia as strategic competitors in its new defense strategy announced earlier this year , according to a report on the website of the british " Jane 's defense weekly . "
since then , the United States Navy has revived the Second Fleet in order to confront Russia more directly .
the move has raised some doubts and concerns among allies and analysts that the US Navy could move away from the &quot; Asia @-@ Pacific rebalancing &quot; strategy that has marked the Obama administration , the report said .
but Admiral Moran said the U. S. Navy &apos;s focus remains on the western Pacific .
at a round @-@ table discussion entitled &quot; Addressing the High Seas Challenge , &quot; hosted by the National Bureau of Asian Studies of the United States in Washington , D.C. , on 24 January 2018 , he said : &quot; there has been no significant change for us . &quot;
&quot; the emphasis is still on rebalancing , shifting the center of gravity or whatever you want to describe it , &quot; Moran said .
however , he acknowledged that the united states has close ties with europe .
&quot; we will continue to look at the growth of the West Coast and balance what we can do , &quot; he said .
although Moran pointed out that the overall policy toward russia falls within the purview of the us secretary of defense , he warned : " the Russians may face demographic and economic challenges , but history has proven that if we clash with them , they will be very tough . "
Admiral Moran said that , as part of the us resurgence against russia , china , and other competitors , the us navy is dynamically deploying its troops into a " new mode of operation , " which will help to surprise opponents about where the us aircraft carrier combat group or other assets will be deployed at any given time and place .
he said : " we in the navy and marines support it - the concept of unpredictability of operations , not appearing in the same place again and again , almost like a hairpin - this is our practice . "
the first attempt at such a new approach was reported to have been made by the carrier battle group Harri Truman , whose early deployment included working visits to ports and patrolling in areas normally reserved for passage .
Moran said the U.S. Navy was working to ensure allies knew the ships would still patrol traditional areas and was addressing logistical and family liaison issues for the new deployment procedures .
Lieutenant General Michael Nunan , commander of the Royal Australian Navy , also spoke at the event , saying the Australian army could work seamlessly with the United States aircraft carrier battle group .
he said the situation would continue as the Royal Australian Navy planned to procure nine more frigates equipped with the aegis combat system .
more airlines raise or restore fuel surcharges from Oct. 5 It &apos;s going to be more expensive for a plane trip starting next Friday
yesterday , Xiang Peng airlines , Okai airlines , and other airlines announced to the public that as of october 5 , 2018 ( the date of issuance of tickets ) , the domestic flight fuel surcharge will be $ 20 per passenger for the routes below 800 km , and $ 30 per passenger for the routes above 800 km .
Xiang Peng airlines , Okai airlines , and others announced that starting from 0 : 00 a.m . on october 5 , 2018 ( the date of issue ) , the standard for charging fuel surcharges for domestic air routes below 800 km ( including ) will be raised from 10 yuan per person to 20 yuan per person , and the standard for charging fuel surcharges for domestic air routes above 800 km will be raised from 10 yuan per passenger to 30 yuan per person .
children , military and police disabled persons are all $ 10 per person ; infants continue to be exempt .
according to the person in charge of the flight ticket , the airline has indicated in the notice that the fuel surcharge will be levied on the original date of issue , and the fuel surcharge will not be refunded when the ticket is changed .
this means that domestic airline tickets issued before 5 October will not be subject to the new standard fuel surcharge if they are changed to 5 October inclusive .
since June 5 , 2018 , Air China , East China Airlines , Sea Airways , Shanghai Airlines , Chunqiu Airlines , Shenzhen Airlines , Western Airlines , Okai Airlines and other airlines have resumed charging fuel surcharges for domestic routes that have been cancelled for three years , at a rate of 10 yuan per person .
this time , Xiang Peng airlines and Okai airlines took the lead in announcing an increase in the fuel surcharge . as of the time of writing , we have not seen any news from the four major domestic airlines announcing that they would follow up on the readjustment .
it has also been learned that the hong kong civil aviation department ( cad ) has stipulated that airlines are free to decide whether or not to charge a fuel surcharge from november .
Cathay Pacific first announced on Sept . 27 that it would reintroduce the fuel surcharge from Nov 2 .
Cathay pacific airways ' website shows that all Cathay pacific airways and Cathay pacific dragon airfares issued or re - issued on or after november 2 will include fuel surcharges for long - haul flights to and from hong kong and the southwest pacific region , north america , europe , the middle east and india , and africa , with fuel surcharges of $ 652 and $ 146 for short - haul flights .
the cost is applicable to all types of tickets and is calculated on the basis of each segment and includes airfares quoted in all direct selling channels of Cathay Pacific .
on the eve of the 69 th anniversary of the founding of the people 's republic of china , chinese state council premier li Keqiang met with new ambassadors from 29 countries and regions at the great hall of the people on the afternoon of 30 april .
Li Keqiang shook hands and cordially talked with all diplomatic envoys in china .
Li Keqiang welcomed the ambassadors to take up their new posts in china , and asked them to convey sincere greetings and best wishes to the leaders and people of all relevant countries and leaders of relevant organizations .
Li keqiang spoke positively of china 's good relations with other countries and regions , stressing that china is committed to enhancing bilateral political mutual trust , deepening practical cooperation , and strengthening coordination and cooperation in international and regional affairs . he hoped that the special envoys would go more frequently , look more closely , and make new positive contributions to promoting the development of china 's relations with their respective countries and regions in their new posts .
the chinese government is willing to provide convenience and support to the ambassadors in the performance of their duties .
Li Keqiang pointed out : China adheres to the road of peaceful development and unswervingly promotes economic globalization .
this year marks the 40th anniversary of china 's reform and opening up . as the largest developing country in the world , we are willing to achieve common development with other countries in further opening up .
against the background of rising protectionism and unilateralism , we are willing to work with all sides to continue to consolidate and strengthen our partnership in line with the principles of mutual respect , equality and mutual benefit , to promote the strategy of reciprocal development , to promote cooperation in the construction of the &quot; one belt , one road , &quot; to join hands in safeguarding multilateralism and free trade , to build an open world economy , and to inject new impetus into the stable and balanced development of the world economy .
the ambassadors of various countries and institutions in china warmly congratulated the 69 th anniversary of the founding of the people 's republic of china , conveyed greetings from the leaders of their respective countries and institutions to the chinese leaders and people , and expressed the belief that further deepening reform and opening up in the future will bring more development opportunities to the world .
we are willing to play a positive role in promoting friendly cooperation between our respective countries and regions and in achieving a better mutual benefit and win - win situation .
subsequently , foreign envoys to china attended the national day reception at the invitation of li keqiang .
Wang Yi , State Councilor and Minister for Foreign Affairs , attended the event .
Ito Tzu , Japan , acknowledged a $ 1.3 billion impairment in its investment in CITIC China on Friday , writing down its biggest corporate investment deal as a result of trade tensions between China and the United States .
in May 2016 , in Tokyo , Japan , a man walks past the headquarters of Pu Hong Co . Ltd .
Mr Pinghong said the trade war had hit his U. S. cereal arm , Mr Gao Hong , and that it had suspended financial transactions in agriculture .
some Japanese manufacturers of heavy equipment and telecoms companies have already warned about the impact of trade frictions between china and the united states when announcing their latest results , and these Japanese trading houses have now joined the ranks .
the US and China impose tariffs on each other &apos;s hundreds of billions of dollars in goods , and US President Donald Trump has threatened to extend the tax to all Chinese exports of more than $ 500 billion if the dispute is not resolved .
Tsuyoshi Hachimura , Ito &apos;s commercial treasurer , said the trade dispute could have a bigger impact on China &apos;s economy next year .
Ito Zhong Commercial and Thailand &apos;s Bumble Group invested $ 10 billion in CITIC in 2015 , taking a 20 per cent stake .
Hachimura said Ito Tzu had a 143.3 billion yen ( $ 1.3 billion ) loss on the stake because it was not expected that CITIC &apos;s share price would rebound in the near future .
Ito Tzu maintained its profit forecast for the fiscal year ending March 31 , 2019 at 500 billion yen .
China imposed a 25 per cent import tariff on American soybeans in July to counter Washington &apos;s trade frictions .
&quot; our cereal business has been hit by trade frictions between the US and China , &quot; said Yuanhong Pak , chief financial officer .
Mr Gao said he had stopped trading in his own accounts since September .
in a draft statement Friday , Gaohong spokesman Pat Burke said the company was &quot; constrained by internal policies and a lack of market opportunities . &quot;
he also said the suspension of financial transactions would not lead to job losses .
Pak Hong maintained its annual profit forecast of 230 billion yen , helped by pulp and paper production and power generation .
Sumitomo Commercial reported Thursday a 16 per cent rise in profits from April to September , emphasizing that &quot; US @-@ China trade problems have led to unclear prospects . &quot;
Mitsubishi Commercial raised its annual profit estimate to record levels Friday as a result of increased coke production and higher prices for commodities such as oil and coal .
Mitsubishi Commercial also announced a new business plan to boost profits to 900 billion yen ( $ 7.98 billion ) in the fiscal year ending March 31 , 2022 , from an estimated 640 billion yen this year .
chinanews , november 5 ( chinanews ) according to a comprehensive report , voting in the us mid - term elections has entered the countdown .
on November 4 , President Donald Trump and his Democratic opponents actively &quot; urged &quot; their core constituencies to vote .
both parties point out that voter turnout will be the key to the outcome .
it has been reported that , 48 hours before the popular vote in the United States , Trump was busy attending a rally for Republican candidates , while former President Barack Obama went to Indiana to stand on the platform for Joe Donnelly , the Democratic senate candidate who was anxious about the election , and to shout his final pre @-@ election demands to the crowd .
on November 4 , Trump went to Megon , Georgia , to stand for the Republican candidate for governor , Brian Kemp , saying : &quot; you have to go to the polling station on Tuesday , you have to vote . &quot;
&quot; the contrast between the elections is unlikely to be clearer . &quot;
voter political enthusiasm has risen to a rare peak , with early voting in some states far more than usual .
successive US presidents face their first midterm elections , and the number of congressional seats in his party tends to fall .
Republicans could benefit from an economic assessment and Trump &apos;s tight focus on border security , although the Democratic Party &apos;s federal House of Representatives election remains strong , according to a new poll published on Thursday by The Washington Post and ABC News .
polls show that registered voters prefer more Democratic House candidates than Republicans , at 50 % to 43 % , but are still down 14 percentage points ahead of August .
another poll by the National Broadcasting Corporation ( NBC ) and The Wall Street Journal also showed Democrats still 7 percentage points ahead of Republicans .
&quot; when people don &apos;t tell the truth , when words don &apos;t represent anything anymore , it &apos;s bound to be a bad thing , &quot; Obama told the crowd during Senator Donoli &apos;s campaign .
democracy does not work when people have to lie to themselves . &quot;
&quot; the only way to stop these Republicans now is for you and your votes . &quot;
Democrats face the most difficult election in decades in the Senate , where Republicans now hold more than half of the 51 seats .
but the House of Representatives is in a better position , with Democrats needing an additional 23 seats to take control of the 435 @-@ seat House .
analysts at FiveThirty Eight.com , the forecasters , predict that Democrats will win as much as 85 % of the House of Representatives .
the CPPCC national committee convened general secretary xi Jinping 's important ideological and theoretical seminar on strengthening and improving the CPPCC 's work . Wang yang attended and delivered a speech .
the national committee of the chinese people 's political consultative conference ( CPPCC ) held an important ideological and theoretical seminar on strengthening and improving CPPCC work in beijing from 29 to 30 august .
Wang yang , member of the standing committee of the political bureau of the CPC central committee and chairman of the CPPCC national committee , attended and spoke at the meeting .
he emphatically pointed out : General secretary xi Jinping 's important thinking on strengthening and improving the work of the CPPCC profoundly expounded the role , objectives , duties , missions , and practical requirements of the CPPCC , scientifically answered a series of major questions of a directional , overall , and strategic nature , and was a powerful ideological weapon guiding the work of the CPPCC in the new era .
it is necessary to conscientiously study and implement this important thinking , grasp its great significance , enrich its connotation , and spiritual essence , conscientiously make efforts to study , understand , and understand , and do practical work to improve the quality of the work of the CPPCC through theoretical study and ideological armament , and conscientiously undertake the new tasks of the CPPCC in the new era .
from 29 to 30 september , the national committee of the chinese people 's political consultative conference [ CPPCC ] held in beijing an important ideological and theoretical seminar on strengthening and improving the CPPCC work .
Wang yang pointed out : since the 18 th CPC national congress , general secretary Xi Jinping has put forward a series of new ideas and new viewpoints on strengthening and improving the work of the CPPCC . for the first time , he has put forward that the CPPCC is an important channel and special consultative body for socialist consultation and democracy , an important component of the state management system , and an institutional arrangement with chinese characteristics . he has for the first time expounded the characteristics and advantages of the new party system .
Wang yang stressed : the CPPCC committees at all levels should take theoretical study and discussion as an opportunity to further find out the weak links and shortcomings in the CPPCC 's work , make efforts to strengthen and improve it , and seek breakthroughs .
it is necessary to comprehensively strengthen party building in the CPPCC system and ensure that the party central committee 's decision - making and arrangements are implemented to the letter in the CPPCC work .
we should strengthen ideological and political leadership , improve the system , procedures , and mechanisms for making suggestions and for building consensus on " two - way power , " and implement ideological and political leadership in all aspects and in the entire process of performing our duties .
it is necessary to focus on the central task , perform duties and responsibilities , better obey and serve the overall interests of the party and the state , improve the quality of advisors , and enhance the effectiveness of performing duties .
it is necessary to strengthen the CPPCC 's own construction , do a good job in educating and training its members and cadres , give play to the basic role of the special committee , and lay a solid foundation for the CPPCC to carry out its duties .
it is necessary to strengthen guidance for the work of the local CPPCC , demonstrate the direction , solve difficult problems , and raise the overall level of the work of the CPPCC .
in order to thoroughly study and implement the thinking of Xi Jinping on socialism with chinese characteristics in the new era and the spirit of the 19 th CPC national congress , the CPPCC national committee system began in may to launch general secretary Xi Jinping 's important ideological study and discussion activities on strengthening and improving the work of the CPPCC . it held eight regional forums and seven expert and academic forums , and identified 18 key topics and six basic theoretical topics . a total of 793,800 CPPCC members at all levels and 279,000 cadres participated in studying and formed more than 36,000 research papers .
Renmin ribao beijing , november 5 ( Wang xiaoyan ) under the current wave of " mass entrepreneurship , mass innovation , " more and more scientific and technological companies have begun to attach importance to patent research and development and related protection work , dig deeply into the potential value of patents , and occupy market dominance .
in the same way , many scientific and technological enterprises have encountered a great deal of infringement in the areas of patent technology licensing and the use of patent technology .
at the end of 2017 , Tan Wei , He Zhanghong and Lai Bin from Guangdong Province sued Guangdong Pacific Internet Information Services Limited ( Guangdong Pacific ) , the developer of the &quot; Drop @-@ Drop Travel &quot; APP , to the Guangzhou Intellectual Property Court on the grounds of patent infringement .
the plaintiff asked the court to order that the defendant immediately stop manufacturing , selling , promising to sell and using the plaintiff &apos;s patent .
on October 30 , 2018 , China Refereeing Instruments Network announced the &quot; First Instance Civil Ruling Letter of Patent Infringement Dispute between Tan Wei , He Zhanghong and Beijing Tangerine Technology Co . , Ltd . , &quot; disclosing details of some of the cases in which the APP was sued for patent infringement .
the three plaintiffs held that the patentee and inventor of the patent for the " mobile terminal - based car pooling service system and method " and that the entire operation process of the " windward " application in the " drip trip " APP corresponded to the technical scheme of patent protection involved and constituted patent infringement .
however , during the court 's ruling , citrus science and technology held that Guangdong pacific was not a suitable defendant , that it only provided free downloads of the APP " drip travel " involved in the case on the internet , that it did not implement the patent method involved , that there was no direct or indirect infringement , and that it should not be classified as a defendant in this case .
secondly , the tort in this case is not in Guangdong .
in accordance with the law , the place of infringement of the patent in question was the place where the patent method in question was carried out in its entirety . therefore , the court jurisdiction was challenged and the case was transferred to the court where the defendant resides , namely , the beijing intellectual property court .
the Guangzhou intellectual property court held that it was not inappropriate for the plaintiff to list the defendant , Guangdong Pacific , as the defendant had provided the alleged infringing travel APP products on its internet platform .
and the defendant Guangdong Pacific domicile in Guangzhou City , under the jurisdiction of the Guangzhou Intellectual Property Court .
the defendant , Little Tangerine Technology , argued that the case should be referred to the Beijing Intellectual Property Court for trial on insufficient grounds , rejected the objection of the defendant , Little Tangerine Technology Co . , Ltd . , to the jurisdiction of the case and bore the costs of accepting the challenge .
other trials of the case have not yet been announced , and reporters will pay close attention to the details of the case .
interview with Chief Executive Officer , Federal Scientific and Industrial Research Organisation of Australia : Australia @-@ China Science and Technology Cooperation Achieves Outstanding Results
" China 's science and technology have developed rapidly in the past few decades , and australia and china can achieve fruitful results by working hand in hand in the scientific field . "
in an exclusive interview with zxs in beijing a few days ago , Larry Marshall , chief executive officer of australia 's federal scientific and industrial research organization , said : from dealing with climate change to cooperation in the " eye of heaven " project , australia - china cooperation in the field of science and technology has shown great vitality .
CSIRO , Australia &apos;s largest national research institute , has produced a number of innovative research results that have attracted worldwide attention in the areas of oceans , energy , biology , materials and astronomy .
CSIRO and the Chinese Academy of Sciences and other scientific research institutions have maintained close cooperation .
&quot; this is a lasting friendship , one that embraces a tradition of trust in partners and long @-@ term cooperation , &quot; Marshall said .
in May , China &apos;s 500 @-@ meter spherical radio telescope , China &apos;s Heaven Eye , installed the world &apos;s first 19 @-@ beam L @-@ band receiver .
the most advanced 19 - beam feed receiver in the world is jointly developed by chinese and Australian scientists .
Marshall said the successful development of the receiver was based on CSIRO &apos;s years of technological accumulation , which would increase the speed of the FAST survey by five to six times and expand the range of scientific observation targets .
&quot; this is CSIRO &apos;s contribution to FAST . &quot;
in addition to the above @-@ mentioned cooperation , CSIRO also cooperates closely with Chinese scientific institutions in the construction of a square kilometre array of radio telescopes , the development of new fuel technologies and the conservation and reduction of emissions .
&quot; previous scientific research has tended to focus on problems over a hundred years from now , and now more scientific research is needed to solve the problems that lie ahead . &quot;
Marshall held that australia and china are complementary in the field of scientific development , and that both countries face a series of challenges in their development .
for example , extreme weather is common around the globe , droughts and floods have led to reduced food production and food shortages have severely affected human development .
at the same time , population explosion , aging , chronic diseases and other issues are also serious challenges .
" the cooperation between australia and china in recent years has mainly focused on solving these current problems . "
Marshall said that the international center for marine research in the southern hemisphere , jointly set up by CSIRO and the Qingdao national laboratory for marine science and technology , will focus on observing the El Niño and La Niña phenomena , studying their relationship with extreme weather , and establishing early warning facilities for extreme weather . CSIRO and the chinese academy of science and technology have jointly developed new grain varieties to overcome extreme weather and can also alleviate the food shortage caused by extreme weather .
&quot; in the current environment , where it is difficult for science , technology and innovation to be accomplished on their own , where the costs are extremely high and where there are so many problems to be solved , cooperation is particularly important today . &quot;
Marshall said that the closer the cooperation , the more likely it will be to achieve breakthrough progress , which is also the significance of strengthening cooperation between australia and china under the " one belt , one road " framework .
" to strengthen bilateral cooperation , it is mainly in the field of science and technology . "
Marshall said , for example , that CSIRO had recently developed a non @-@ cyanide gold purification method . because the traditional cyanide gold purification method was very harmful to the environment , many countries wanted to find a way to purify gold that was less polluting to the environment .
" we are very willing to introduce this technology into china , which is one of the results of our participation in the ' one belt , one road ' cooperation . "
on 29 august , the 2018 baoji silk road tourism promotion and cooperation seminar was held in Urumqi city , Xinjiang . while appreciating the fruits of baoji 's development , guests attending the meeting were also able to enjoy local cuisine and experience the rich local history and culture .
during the month preceding the event , baoji successively launched a series of high - density and extensive tourism promotion activities in eight cities along the silk road , including Tianshui , ping , Lanzhou , Yinchuan , gu yuan , Xining , Zhang ye , and Hami , laying a good foundation for the successful holding of the baoji silk road tourism promotion and project cooperation forum in 2018 .
Hui jincai , mayor of baoji city in Shaanxi province , said : Baoji has a long history and culture , and has a strong industrial foundation . it is the second largest city in Shaanxi province and the second - center city of Guan tien economic zone and Guanzhong plain urban agglomeration . it is an important node city along the " one belt , one road " initiative .
in recent years , Baoji city has continuously upgraded its five major functions of industrial cluster , logistics hub , comprehensive service , open heights , and humanities , and has accelerated its catch - up and high - quality development .
at the meeting , the baoji city tourism development committee and Urumqi tourism bureau signed an agreement on strategic cooperation in tourism between the two places .
at the same time , many travel agencies in Xinjiang signed agreements on cooperation in tourism with Baoji Daishuichuan , Fumen Monastery Buddha Cultural Scenic Area , Taibaishan Tourism Scenic Area and Guantan Prairie Scenic Area .
Chen Hongwei , head of the marketing promotion section of the baoji city tourism development committee , said : " some tourist resources in Xinjiang are complementary to baoji . we have come all the way to promote tourism in Xinjiang , mainly introducing the humanistic baoji , gourmet baoji , natural scenery , and so on . more than 500 photos have been selected so that the tourists can feel the beautiful scenery of baoji . "
focusing on tourism resources , tourism projects , and tourist routes , the event comprehensively publicized and promoted the overall image of baoji tourism , high - quality tourism products , and fine - quality tourism industry projects , consolidated Xinjiang 's tourist source market , comprehensively sang the brand name of " seeing china coming to baoji , " and promoted the influence of baoji in northwest china 's Xinjiang to attract more tourists and tourists .
Feng Xu , deputy director of the baoji city merchants and merchants bureau , said : " at this event , baoji city departments at all levels , counties , districts , and development zones actively held docking talks and coordinated the implementation of a large number of good projects and large projects .
so far , 41 projects have been signed , involving a total amount of 26.043 billion yuan . "
in recent years , around the goal of building international cities along the " one belt , one road , one road " initiative , famous cities in the equipment manufacturing industry , famous historical and cultural cities , and beautiful and happy cities with livable occupations , Baoji has continuously promoted the five major functions of industrial clusters , logistics hubs , integrated services , open highlands , and humanities , speeding up catch - up and surpassing and high - quality development .
in 2017 , the regional gross domestic product reached 218 billion yuan , up 8.7 percent .
he has won more than 20 national - level honors , including the national civilized city , the national eco - park city , and the china Habitat environment award .
Yan naimin , standing committee member and vice mayor of Urumqi city CPC committee , introduced that Urumqi , as a key town in the new north road on the silk road , has a special geographical location advantage . since ancient times , Urumqi has been an important channel linking the north and the south of the Tianshan mountains , connecting Xinjiang with the hinterland , and connecting china with central asia , west asia , and europe . it has been an important window for china 's opening up to the west and for foreign economic and cultural exchanges , and has a favorable investment environment .
focusing on equipment manufacturing , logistics trade , and tourism industries , the event was held in Urumqi with the sincere intention of seeking common development opportunities and discussing major plans for cooperation .
at the meeting , local businessmen in Xinjiang signed six contracts with baoji counties and districts , involving 3.25 billion yuan .
on the same day , foreign guests , including representatives of Kyrgyzstan 's visa office in Urumqi , russia 's Novosibirsk law company limited , the Tajik chamber of commerce and industry in Urumqi , and the russian Tatarstan chamber of commerce , attended the meeting .
the Urumqi Merchants Bureau , Commercial Bureau , Agricultural and Pastoral Bureau , Tourism Bureau , and other departments , enterprises and the media attended the meeting .
the rejuvenation of the northeast is related to the overall situation of national development .
the industrial enterprises in northeast china are bigger and have a better foundation . for northeast china , grasping innovation means grasping development , and seeking innovation means grasping the future .
whether or not the vitality of the old industrial base can be re - energized and released will affect the general secretary 's heart .
North Korea &apos;s foreign minister , Lee Yong @-@ ho , told the United Nations Saturday that the continued imposition of sanctions is deepening North Korea &apos;s mistrust of the United States and that North Korea cannot give up its nuclear weapons unilaterally under such circumstances .
Lee Yong @-@ ho told the United Nations General Assembly that North Korea had adopted &quot; very friendly practices &quot; over the past year , including halting missile and nuclear tests , dismantling nuclear testing sites and committing to non @-@ proliferation of nuclear weapons and technology .
&quot; but we have not seen any response from the United States , &quot; he said .
" if we do not trust the united states , we will have no confidence in our national security , and under such circumstances , we cannot give up weapons unilaterally first . "
although lee yonhao repeated north korea 's complaints about the united states ' opposition to " phased " denuclearization , his remarks were of great significance because he did not completely reject unilateral denuclearization , as north korea had done before .
Lee referred to a joint statement by Kim Jong @-@ un and Trump on June 12 , when Kim Jong @-@ un agreed to work toward &quot; denuclearizing the Korean peninsula &quot; and Trump promised to protect North Korea &apos;s security .
North Korea has been seeking an official end to the 1950 @-@ 53 Korean War , but the United States says North Korea must first give up its nuclear weapons .
the united states also refused to relax its demand for international sanctions against north korea .
" the united states insists on " denuclearizing first , " and has increased the pressure for sanctions to achieve its goal through high pressure . it has even refused to issue a " declaration on the end of the war , " li yonhao said .
&quot; the idea that sanctions can make us kneel for mercy is that people who do not know us are daydreaming .
but the problem is that these continuing sanctions are deepening our mistrust .
Lee yung - ho did not mention the us president 's second special fund meeting plan mentioned at the united nations earlier this week .
instead , he highlighted Kim Jong @-@ un &apos;s three meetings with South Korean President Wen Jin @-@ yun over the past five months , and said : &quot; the denuclearization of the Korean peninsula would not have become so deadlocked if the other side had been South Korea , not North Korea . &quot;
China announced a reduction in import tariffs for 1,585 tariff items effective 1 November 2018 .
since the beginning of this year , china has taken the initiative to lower import tariffs one after another .
on 1 may this year , the taxes on pharmaceuticals were reduced in an all - round way , and the import tariffs on all ordinary pharmaceuticals , including anti - cancer pharmaceuticals , alkaloids , and proprietary chinese medicines , which were actually imported , were adjusted to zero .
at the same time , it also greatly reduced the value - added tax on the production and import of anti - cancer drugs .
July 1 reduces taxes on 218 taxable cars and parts .
after the tax cut , china 's vehicle tax rate has been lower than the average in developing countries , and is in line with the actual conditions of china 's automobile industry .
this tax reduction will promote the readjustment of the industrial structure and the optimal allocation of resources , speed up the survival of the fittest and fittest , and help improve the quality of products and services . it is expected to promote the readjustment of automobile prices to a certain extent so that consumers can reap more tangible benefits .
July 1 th reduced taxes on 1,449 items of daily consumer goods .
the reduction of taxes on consumer goods for daily use is closely related to the people &apos;s need for a better life .
this time the tax cut was not only large but also strong , with the average tax cut reaching 56 percent .
the reduction of taxes on consumer goods for daily use directly benefits the vast number of consumers and promotes the competitiveness of domestic industries .
on Nov. 1 , taxes will be reduced on 1,585 items of machinery and electrical equipment , parts and raw materials , and other industrial products .
appropriately lowering import tariffs on some badly needed domestic industrial products will attract more foreign investment , help increase effective domestic supply and promote industrial upgrading , help enterprises allocate resources on a global scale , reduce production costs , and help reduce pressure on the domestic environment .
according to a relevant person in charge of the office of the customs and excise commission under the state council , the above - mentioned four autonomous tax reductions and the third - step tax reduction implemented on 1 july this year on the basis of the results of negotiations on expanding the scope of the information technology agreement will reduce china 's total tariff level from 9.8 percent in the previous year to 7.5 percent .
the adjusted total tariff level is slightly higher than that of the eu , lower than that of most developing countries , and is at a moderate low level , basically matching china 's position as a developing country and its stage of development .
according to the responsible person , the total tariff level , as one of the important indexes of china 's open trade in goods , should be commensurate with the stage of china 's economic development and reflect the characteristics of the times .
China 's trade in goods is the largest in the world , and it already has an economic foundation for further opening up . however , the quality and efficiency of trade development are still lagging behind those of developed economies . therefore , the overall level of tariffs should be appropriately lowered .
tariffs are the means of protection for compliance . tariff levels should be commensurate with industrial competitiveness . benign competition should be encouraged . excessive protection is not conducive to industrial development and the improvement of quality .
tariff rate adjustment should take into account the needs of production and consumer demand .
it is necessary to lay stress on lowering the commodity tax rate , which is relatively large in domestic demand and helps the industrial transformation and upgrading . it is necessary to strive to increase the import of products with special advantages where the demand of the masses is concentrated , constantly enhance the sense of enterprise and public access , and meet the needs for upgrading the industrial structure and the consumption structure .
efforts to reduce taxes should take into account fiscal revenues and the affordability of industrial development .
in selecting the specific commodities to be reduced and the scope of the reduction , it is necessary to coordinate well the two markets at home and abroad and the upper and lower levels , and the relations between production and consumption , so as to maintain the momentum of steady and good development of china 's economy .
the responsible person stressed : this year marks the 40 th anniversary of reform and opening up . China 's initiative to lower the overall level of import tariffs is a major move made in line with china 's own need to achieve high - quality development . it is conducive to making overall use of both international and foreign resources , promoting the improvement of the quality of the domestic supply system , and satisfying the people 's needs for consumption and upgrading .
this action and measure shows that china will unswervingly pursue a mutually beneficial and win - win strategy of opening up , firmly support economic globalization , resolutely safeguard the principle of free trade and the multilateral trade system with the wto as the core , continue to draw development momentum from opening up to the world , and enable china to develop and benefit the world better .
Serbian president to meet in kosovo tomorrow to discuss kosovo situation
citing information from the Serbian president 's office , the Yugoslav news agency said that Serbian president Vučić ordered the armed forces of kosovo to reach the highest operational readiness in view of the fact that the special forces of kosovo have occupied the passage of the water storage lake at the gazivoda hydropower station in northern kosovo controlled by the belgrade side .
on 29 September , the Serbian Minister of Defence , Vulin , declared that the Serbian army was on full alert .
Vulin stressed that Serbia would continue to monitor the current situation in Kosovo as long as the orders issued by Vučić remained in force , and that the Serb Army would respond regardless of the direction of events .
according to a russian news agency report , in an interview on 29 september , Vučić said that he had briefed the united states , russia , and europe on the current situation and would travel to Moscow on 2 october to meet with russian president Putin and seek Putin 's support on the kosovo issue .
asked if Serbia needed Russian military support , as Syria did , Vučić answered in the negative : &quot; I do not want a major military conflict on our territory . &quot;
Vučić also stated that the full operational readiness of the Serbian Army was intended only to serve as a deterrent to the conflict , but it was also a clear warning that no violence in Kosovo would be tolerated .
the increase in the operational readiness of the Serbian Army is linked to two major moves by the Kosovo side .
according to the Serbian side , in recent days Albanians have been arresting in the northern part of Kosovo Serbs who have been living there for generations without violating any law .
Vučić said that since Marko Jurić , head of the Serbian government 's office in kosovo and Metohija , was beaten and detained by the kosovo Albanian army on 26 march this year , the ethnic Albanians have escalated the situation in the region and carried out inhuman arrests and expulsions of Serbs .
in addition , more than 100 people , including the ROSU Special Forces of the Ministry of Internal Affairs of the Republic of Kosovo , armed police and snipers , who announced their own establishment a few days ago , occupied positions near the water storage lake at the Gatsivoda hydropower station , entered the ecological and sports centre near the dam in the northern part of the Kosovo region and blocked all nearby roads , which were originally controlled by the Serbian side .
Vučić pointed out : this military adventurous action in kosovo was instigated by western countries . the kosovo army 's move was not notified to the Serbian side beforehand , in violation of chapter 9 , paragraph 1 , of the Brussels agreement , and also in violation of un security council resolution 1244 and the military - technical agreement between Serbia and kosovo .
Vučić has already addressed NATO Secretary @-@ General Stoltenberg , criticizing the hypocrisy of Western countries over Kosovo .
the root cause of the current conflict remains centuries of historical enmity between the Serbian and Albanian communities in Kosovo .
with regard to Kosovo &apos;s affiliation , Serbs and Albanians have different accounts .
Serbia considers Kosovo to be the birthplace of the nation and the cradle of culture , as Serbia established its most powerful State here in the twelfth century , and ethnic Albanians moved in large numbers only after the Ottoman Empire invaded and the Serbian army fell back to the north .
Albanians , for their part , maintained that the primitive Ilirians , who lived in Kosovo in the fourth and fifth centuries BC , were the ancestors of Albanians and , as such , had been Albanian territory since time immemorial .
subjective political divisions have led to violent ethnic , religious and cultural clashes and to violent confrontations between Serbs and Albanians in the Kosovo region .
in 1912 , Kosovo Albanians first declared the independence of Albania .
after the First World War , a large number of Albanians living in the Balkans moved to Turkey , with a relative increase in the proportion of Serbs , who perceived the practice of &quot; taking back only their own land &quot; as looting by Albanians as &quot; Greater Serbia , &quot; fuelling the contradictions between the two communities .
Kosovo has become a " powder keg " in the Balkans .
in 1999 , armed clashes between Albanian separatists in the Kosovo Liberation Army ( KLA ) and the Serbian army and police led to the bombing of the Yugoslav Federal Republic of Serbia and Montenegro by NATO forces and the outbreak of the war in Kosovo .
on 17 February 2008 , Kosovo unilaterally declared its independence from Serbia .
since then , despite reports that Serbia will normalize relations with kosovo and sign a global and legally binding agreement , agreements between the united states , europe , and russia have not been signed because of historical ethnic enmity and geopolitical constraints .
just a month ago , Vučić made it clear for the first time that he was in favour of separating Serbs from Albanians in Kosovo and once again publicizing the contradictions between the two communities .
power communications still suspended amid tsunami rescue difficulties
according to figures released by indonesia 's disaster relief agency early on the morning of the 30 th , a strong earthquake and a tsunami caused 420 deaths in donggara district , central Sulawesi province , on the 28 th .
Wilem Rampangilei , head of the Indonesian Disaster Relief Agency , said the figure was preliminary statistics for the central Sulawesi provincial capital of Palu , about 80 kilometers from the epicenter of the quake , where many hotels , shopping malls , warehouses and other crowded buildings damaged by the earthquake have yet to be rescued because of a lack of large search and rescue equipment .
on September 29 , 2018 , local time , a bridge damaged by an earthquake and tsunami collapsed in Ba Lu , Indonesia , breaking into sections .
as a result of the severe damage to electricity and communications facilities , the epicentre of the earthquake , Dungala District , and the adjacent area of Sigi , remain inaccessible &quot; isolated islands &quot; and the number of victims cannot be counted .
Indonesian Vice President Carla says the death toll may be in the thousands , according to media reports .
power outages , communications outages , road disruptions , airport damage ... Strong earthquakes and post @-@ tsunami rescue efforts have been difficult .
as a result of the power outage , a number of hospitals and rescue settlements in the city of Palu rely on fuel to generate electricity .
roads into and out of the city were blocked by landslides and large transport vehicles , including fuel tankers , were prevented from entering , straining fuel supplies .
Indonesian social minister Agus said emergency relief supplies , including tents , mattresses , blankets , clothing , food and household kits , had not arrived from the neighboring provinces of Surawisi and Gorantaro because of the damage to the roads .
relief consignments from the capital , Jakarta , are being transported to the affected areas by air transport aircraft .
in view of the damage to the tower and runway of Palu airport during the earthquake , all commercial flights have been suspended for the sole purpose of ensuring security and safeguarding relief operations , and military aircraft carrying relief supplies and personnel have taken off and landed .
Indonesian political , legal and security co - ordinator Wiranto , who is in charge of rescue operations in the quake zone , called for an early resumption of power supply and airport commercial flight services to ensure the operation of rescue agencies such as hospitals and allow more aid workers , volunteers and aid supplies to reach the affected areas .
on 28 august , several strong earthquakes occurred successively in donggara county , central Sulawesi province . among them , a magnitude 7.7 strong earthquake at 1702 local time triggered a tsunami , causing major disasters in Palu city , donggara county , and xiji district .
chinanews , beijing , Oct. 1 ( reporter yin li ) - - - - beijing recently continued to open the most beautiful blue sky pattern , attracting thousands of beijing residents to take a fancy picture on a social platform and feel happy while continuously brushing the screen , saying that " under the blue sky and white clouds , " " drunk " and " skyline are the best business cards in beijing . "
since August , Beijing has ushered in the &quot; blue sky . &quot;
inside the capital , people can be seen anywhere , anytime , holding a smartphone , or holding a single - camera to take pictures .
Weibo , Weixin circle of friends and other social platforms , can be seen in the online footage of the Imperial Palace , Tiananmen Gate , Bird &apos;s Nest , Hutong . . . . . . . . . . . . . various types of buildings in the blue sky under the display of different beauty .
some netizens said that such a " large area of scenery " is the best city propaganda film in beijing , while others ridiculed that if such a blue sky was painted for a long time , people with cervical spondylosis would be cured , and some netizens hoped that " this blue sky would be able to spend the summer through winter and make the four seasons of beijing 's skyline very blue . "
why do people in Beijing especially like to sun the blue sky ?
only because the people who lived in this city in the past suffered from fog and haze , they were particularly eager for the blue sky . after the " blue sky defense battle " was launched in beijing and the air quality was continuously improved , the haze became smaller and the blue sky increased . the people looked at the matter with joy in their hearts , and the happiness they gained was even greater .
it was fine in Beijing on National Day .
at 8 : 00 a.m . , the vast majority of the city 's 35 air quality monitoring stations showed " grade 1 excellence " in green .
the spontaneous &quot; Blue Skies &quot; themed photography contest on social platforms continues .
why is the sky so blue in Beijing recently ?
in August , the average concentration of fine particles ( PM2.5 ) in Beijing was 35 ug / m3 , the best in nearly five years , according to the head of the Beijing Environmental Protection Bureau .
the real @-@ time concentration of PM2.5 in September was even more frequent in single digits .
a major factor in the emergence of the " blue sky " lies in the overall favorable weather conditions in the recent period . more importantly , beijing has persistently carried out air pollution control , vigorously promoted the clean air action plan over the past five years , and continuously released environmental benefits , thus reducing the total amount of pollutants emitted in the region . all these have laid the foundation for a sustained improvement in air quality .
the Beijing Clean Air Action Plan 2013 @-@ 2017 was officially launched and implemented in Beijing in 2013 .
under the plan , officials continued to guide non @-@ capital functional decontamination , promote clean energy substitution and pollution abatement , and phase out 4,923 coal @-@ fired boilers .
as a result , beijing has become the first big city in mainland china to realize full natural gas network .
data show that between 2013 and 2017 , the annual average concentration of PM2.5 in Beijing decreased by 35.6 per cent ; the number of days the air quality met the target increased by 50 ; the number of days of first @-@ degree excellence increased by 25 ; and the total number of days of heavy pollution decreased by 35 , with a significant decrease in the incidence of heavy pollution .
while the air quality continues to improve , beijing authorities announced in september this year , based on a new round of analysis of PM2.5 sources , the " beijing three - year action plan for winning the blue sky defense battle , " focusing on the key prevention and control areas such as diesel trucks , dust removal , and volatile organic matter management , optimizing the structure of transportation , the industrial structure , the energy structure , and the land structure , stepping up regional joint defense control , making efforts to strengthen the fine management of urban areas , comprehensively promoting green development , and striving to make the " beijing municipality 's " no longer have its main body " as the most valuable " and the main body .
during this year 's national day golden week , relevant departments , such as the city tourism commission , industry and commerce , city management , and public security , will step up law enforcement inspections of the " one - day tour " market , focusing on the " six black spots " of tourism , and those who violate the law will be given heavier and more severe penalties in accordance with the law .
yesterday morning , the city government held a special meeting to crack down on illegal " one - day trips " and made plans for a special campaign to crack down on illegal " one - day trips . "
it was revealed at the meeting that focusing on the " six black " disorder in which black tickets , black guides , black societies , black cars , black shops , and black networks ' chain of interests intertwined , this city has launched a special campaign to crack down on illegal " one - day trips " since 28 july .
since the launch of the special campaign , the city has received 39 complaints about the " one - day trip , " a decrease of 63 percent over the same period last year . since the beginning of this year , the city has received 270 complaints about the " one - day trip , " a decrease of 62 percent over the same period last year .
in the past two months , the city has seized 248 " black cars , " investigated and punished 158 cases of violation of regulations governing passenger travel , closed down 29 " black shops " and performing arts venues , investigated and punished 13 " black societies " and 27 " black guides , " confiscated 26,000 illegal advertisements , dismantled 31 illegal " one - day tour " billboards , and dealt with 1,789 fake public transport station plates .
through rectification , the chaotic situation of illegal " one - day trips " has been basically checked , and the market order of " one - day trips " has shown a stable and positive trend .
it has been learned that in recent years , this city has constantly intensified the rectification of illegal " one - day tours . "
in 2016 and 2017 , the city tourism commission received 1,612 and 897 complaints about " one - day trips , " a decrease of 79 percent and 44 percent , respectively , over the same period of last year . however , illegal " one - day trips " continued to strike many blows , frequently rebounding , and forming a " six - black " confusion in which the chain of interests , such as black tickets , black guides , black societies , black cars , black shops , and black networks , were intertwined .
in particular , street illegal visitors are known as &quot; black ticket holders , &quot; illegal websites that publish false travel information , &quot; black nets , &quot; travel agencies engaged in illegal &quot; one @-@ day trips &quot; or unqualified organizations or individuals operated by travel agencies , namely &quot; black clubs , &quot; &quot; black guides &quot; hired by &quot; black clubs &quot; who do not have a tourist pass or practice in violation of regulations , &quot; black guides , &quot; vehicles used by them that do not have tourist qualifications or black cars that provide passenger transport services for illegal &quot; one @-@ day trips , &quot; will eventually be brought into the shops . &quot;
during this special operation , the city has continuously stepped up fixed - type inspections and mobile inspections of illegal " one - day trips . " in view of the frequent occurrence of illegal " one - day trips " and the high impact of such illegal " one - day trips " on tourist routes , the departments concerned have sent secretly visiting teams to secretly visit the places . they have discovered evidence of violations of the law and regulations and severely investigated and punished the cases according to law .
among them , " black cars " and " black shops " have become two key points in the special campaign .
it has been learned that without black cars , illegal " one - day trips " cannot take place . black cars are easy to find , remember , and investigate , and are also fixed assets with relatively high individual value .
the relevant departments have used road traffic monitoring probes to increase supervision and control over the major " one - day tour " routes , and the " black cars " can be discovered and dealt with in a timely manner by means of technological intelligence , such as technical defense and material defense .
because of the small number of tourist shopping " black shops , " they operate on land , and have also become the focal points of the crackdown .
in order to strengthen the deterrence and crackdown on illegal " one - day trips , " all functional departments shall , in accordance with the law , mete out heavier and more severe punishments to those found guilty of violating the law and regulations during the special operations .
in august this year , this city also held a seminar on legal issues related to cracking down on illegal " one - day trips , " and discussed measures for combining administrative punishment with conviction .
according to the municipal tourism commission , more regular travel agencies will be encouraged to carry out " one - day tours " in beijing in the future , and the supply of regular " one - day tours " will be increased in order to further squeeze up the space for illegal " one - day tours . " specific plans are still under study .
in addition , the City Tourist Committee constantly improves the Tourist Tourist Tourist Tourist Tourist Tourist Tourist Tourist List Information System to ensure that each team is included in the monitoring of the e @-@ Tourist Tourist Tourist List Platform .
from a tourist symbol to a digital economy symbol , what has been the experience of Wuzhen these years
as the permanent venue of the world internet congress , Wuzhen has drawn attention to how to take over the dividends of the summit .
in the five years since the first world internet congress , the changes in Wuzhen have become apparent to all .
in 2014 , there were only 12 companies in the town with links to the digital economy and the Internet , and by the third quarter of this year there were more than 500 .
this is a microcosm of the development of the digital economy in Wuzhen .
the holding of the internet conference has enabled local enterprises to accept the digital economy at zero distance , inspired by the wave of digitization , and aroused a strong desire for enterprise transformation and upgrading . traditional manufacturers have increased their input and research and development in areas such as machine exchange and intelligent management .
Jiang Wei , secretary of the party committee of Wuzhen , said that Wuzhen will build a new economic empowerment center in the future .
the development of the digital economy cannot do without the support of infrastructure .
this year , Wuzhen launched a 5G pilot project based on the implementation of a 4G communications network and free WiFi coverage .
at the same time , the town of Tongxiang , where Wuzhen is located , as the first county - level city in the country to build a special channel for international internet data , has also become a hot land for the development of the internet industry .
since the first world internet conference , Tongxiang has introduced 565 projects in the digital economy , with a total planned investment of 37.725 billion yuan . in the first three quarters of this year , the total output value of the core manufacturing industry in the digital economy was expected to reach 8.73 billion yuan , an increase of 13 percent over the same period last year .
&quot; formerly Wuzhen was a tourist symbol , and later more drama and cultural symbols . because of the Internet Congress , it is now the symbol of the Internet and the digital economy . &quot;
Sheng yung - jun , secretary of the tongxiang city CPC committee , believes that the dividends of the world internet congress have accumulated over time , so it is even more necessary to build a platform to undertake the superposition and import of talent , projects , technology , and other elements from all sides .
Tongxiang Shen Yi work abroad for 20 years , due to the Internet congregation , return home to start a business .
on 2 december last year , he entered the fourth internet light fair with high - capacity anti - tampering digital technology solutions , and was favored by many customers .
Shen Yi chose to start her own business in Wuzhen not only because of her hometown complex , " in Wuzhen , it is easier to recruit people than i imagined , our application also landed very quickly , and there is our application in Wuzhen 's intelligent parking project . "
a Wuzhen Road , showing the spillover effect of the Internet Congress .
this road that runs through the north and south of Tongxiang is not only a series of tourist attractions but also an industrial road .
with it as the basis , Wuzhendao Kocheng agglomeration area emerged .
this reporter has learned that in the future , Wuzhen road will become the main front for the development of Tongxiang 's industry , taking the lead in applying the achievements of wisdom and medical treatment , wisdom and old - age support , and wisdom and administrative affairs in large numbers , and gathering together 80 percent of the entire city 's gdp industry and many high - level talent .
