active treatment , China 29 weeks and above premature survival rate reached 98 % , has reached the level of developed countries .
chinanews , Shanghai , september 30 ( Chen jing and Luo yanqian ) the state children 's medical center and the pediatric hospital attached to Fudan university disclosed on the 30th that they have introduced advanced Canadian methods into the " china NICU project for improving the prognostic quality of premature babies in hospital . "
the results of the project show that after active treatment , the survival rate of premature babies aged 29 weeks and over in China has reached 98 per cent , reaching the level of developed countries , but there is still much room for improvement in the survival rate of very young premature and premature babies without complications .
for nearly 20 years , the Chinese government has been paying attention to the treatment of newborns .
at present , the infant mortality rate in the Shanghai region has dropped to 3.71 per thousand , significantly lower than the national average , and reaching the advanced level in developed countries .
through four years of unremitting efforts , the &quot; Chinese NICU project to improve the prognostic quality of premature babies in hospital &quot; has greatly improved the quality of life of premature babies .
Professor cao yun , director of the neonatal intensive care unit ( NICU ) of Fudan university 's pediatric hospital , told this reporter : while raising the survival rate of premature babies , paying attention to reducing the quality of survival of premature babies , reducing the incidence of complications , improving the prognosis of neurodevelopment , and improving the overall outcome of sick children are of great significance to improving the overall quality of life and population of premature babies . they are also important issues of concern to the pediatric and neonatal science circles at home and abroad . at the same time , they are also the key issues of concern to this project .
through four years of unremitting efforts to include tens of thousands of premature babies aged 33 weeks or less , the NICU project has led to a 1 / 3 drop in the mortality rate of infants and premature babies with low birth weight in China , and a significant decrease in the incidence of serious complications among premature babies , which has greatly improved the quality of life of premature babies .
through the establishment of a national network for the improvement of the quality of newborns , the project introduced the concept of cooperative quality improvement , radiated 25 cooperative hospitals throughout China , and set up a set of coordinated , comprehensive , systematic and effective methods for improving the prognosis of premature babies and raising the level of treatment of newborns .
Fudan University &apos;s Pediatric Hospital is working with the National Neonatal Unit to develop guidelines for the diagnosis and treatment of neonatal infections , based on the project &apos;s accumulated experience , in order to provide reference and guidance for the standardized diagnosis and treatment of neonatal infections in China .
it has been learned that in the " project to improve the prognostic quality of premature babies in china , " the pediatric hospital introduced the EPIQ method into 25 large - scale NICUs in 19 provinces across the country , and worked to solve the problem of premature infant infections that plague china 's neonatal care units .
after more than a decade of continuous improvement , Canada &apos;s national survival rate for premature babies has risen by about a third , and Canada is now one of the most prognostic countries in the world .
the EPIQ method has now been applied across Canada to all NICUs and has been adopted in six countries .
two years after the EPIQ intervention , preterm infections fell by 35 percent , while antibiotic use fell by 20 percent , Pediatric Hospital said .
in the future , the Pediatric Hospital attached to Fudan University will continue to popularize and implement the methodology nationwide , with a view to comprehensively reducing the incidence of all complications in premature babies and improving the quality of care for newborns throughout the country .
at present , it is an indisputable fact that there are differences and inequalities in the level of treatment in all parts of China .
according to professor cao yun , as an important construction unit of the national children 's medical center , the pediatric hospital will play a leading role in radiation . this study covers many western provinces , including Xinjiang , Guizhou , Gansu , and Shaanxi , with a view to gradually promoting homogenization and standardization of neonatal treatment throughout the country .
it has been learned that the pediatric hospital affiliated to Fudan university is uniting with the national neonatal force to draw up guidelines for the diagnosis and treatment of neonatal infections based on the accumulated experience of the project , so as to provide reference and guidance for the standardized diagnosis and treatment of neonatal infections in china .
according to sources , in 2019 , the china neonatal cooperative network , which is located at the pediatric hospital affiliated with Fudan university , will carry out the next stage of national quality improvement in association with 63 hospitals across the country , with a view to promoting the uniform development of china 's neonatal treatment level .
Wu jinglei , director of the Shanghai municipal health and family planning committee , said : Shanghai can become a central city in asia not only because of research , but also because the construction of the entire service system , the quality of the service , and the results of the service should have a place in asia so as to truly reflect china 's medical level .
Xin Yiping : erect the &quot; Hero Monument &quot; in your heart - written on the fifth martyr &apos;s day .
on 30 september , on the eve of the 69 - year - old birthday of the republic , we ushered in the fifth anniversary of the martyrs . Xi Jinping and other party and state leaders came to Tiananmen square to attend a flower basket presentation ceremony for the people 's heroes .
at this moment , wherever you are , please pay tribute to the heroes .
Memorial Day , is the recollection , but also awakens .
turning over the heavy history , behind the names of every martyr is a living life .
they also have fiery youth , sincere love , and concerned family members .
however , because they firmly believe that &quot; the doctrine we believe in is the truth of the universe , &quot; they are willing to sacrifice everything they have in order to &quot; save the next generation from suffering . &quot;
" as long as i live , i will cry out for china . "
passing through time and space , the heroes erected a spiritual signpost to guide the way forward .
where do you come from and where do you go ? what kind of people do you come from ? what kind of people do you come from ?
in memory of the heroes , the most important thing is to erect a " heroic monument " in the mind .
according to incomplete statistics , since the revolutionary war years , some 20 million martyrs have sacrificed their lives for national independence , people 's liberation , and the country 's prosperity and strength .
for various reasons , many martyrs did not even leave their names .
countless heroes watered their ideals with blood , practiced their faith with their lives , remembered their names , and passed on their spirits , that is , guarding the roots and souls of the nation .
this &quot; Heroic Monument &quot; cannot be defiled or destroyed .
for some time , historical nihilism , pan - entertainment and other surges .
all kinds of practices that distort history , demean heroes , challenge the conscience of justice , misjudge value judgments , and arouse the public indignation and vigilance of the whole society .
heroes must not be desecrated , heroes must not forget .
we must not allow ourselves to touch the bottom line . we must dare to light our swords and defend the dignity of our heroes with justice and the rule of law .
on 1 may this year , the heroic martyrs protection law came into effect .
judging from judicial practice , the verdicts in some cases are very heartening , effectively safeguarding the glorious image of the heroes in accordance with the law , and releasing positive energy to worship heroes and admire martyrs .
an aspiring people cannot be without heroes , and an ideal country cannot be without pioneers .
remembering the martyrs and calling for heroes have become a common social consensus .
at present , there are over one million memorial facilities of various kinds throughout the country , and more than 100 million people visit and admire martyrs ' mausoleum every year .
the heart is the strongest foundation .
this will make it possible for heroes to be worshipped , heroes to be defended , heroes to learn , heroes to care for , heroes to be brought into the blood of the nation , and a " monument to heroes " will be erected between heaven and earth and deep in the hearts of the people .
Brussels ( Reuters ) - The European Union took a non @-@ confrontational stance on Italy on Friday , following Italy &apos;s defiance of European Union demands to surprise markets with a massive budget deficit plan , but may take a more aggressive stance if Italy insists on too ambitious a goal .
Italy &apos;s skeptical government aims to run a budget deficit equivalent to 2.4 per cent of gross domestic product ( GDP ) over the next three years , suggesting that there has been no debt reduction despite the need to reduce the deficit .
" we have no interest in the crisis between the commission and italy , " said eu executive committee on economic affairs mos corvisi on friday , and he reacted cautiously because eu proposals and sanctions may have little impact on italy .
EU officials and diplomats remain hopeful that market forces will persuade Italy to adjust its budget plan before it is formally presented to the European Commission in mid @-@ October .
after the government announced its plans , the euro fell to its lowest level in nearly two weeks on Friday , and Italian bond yields hit their highest level in three weeks .
if the deficit target remains unchanged until the October deadline , the European Commission may veto Italy &apos;s draft budget , something it has never done to any country .
Italy &apos;s current fiscal plan &quot; does not seem to be in line with the Stability and Growth Pact , &quot; European Commission Vice @-@ President Dumblovsky told a meeting in the Latvian capital Riga later Friday , referring to EU fiscal rules .
but he did not say how this would trigger a reaction from the European Union .
tenderers may submit their applications for the open tender before october 26 this year .
before that , russia 's ministry of agriculture regarded china as one of russia 's priority markets for agricultural exports .
the russian agricultural supervision bureau announced in may that russia 's grain exports to china this agricultural year exceeded one million tons for the first time , setting a new record .
the agency predicts that China may be among the top 10 Russian food importers .
chinanews , Sapporo , september 30 , china 's women 's volleyball team defeated turkey again by 3 : 0 on the 30th after winning Cuba 's first game at 3 : 0 , reaping two consecutive victories in the world championships in 2018 .
but compared with the first battle , the Chinese women &apos;s volleyball team this battle is more difficult .
a total of 24 teams participated in the 2018 Women &apos;s Volleyball World Championships , while the Chinese Women &apos;s Volleyball Association joined Italy , Turkey , Bulgaria , Canada and Cuba in Group B.
Turkey and italy are china 's main rivals in terms of their world rankings and overall strength .
after the start of the game , the chinese team entered the game relatively quickly and gained the lead at the beginning . it maintained its superiority throughout the game , putting pressure on its opponents in serving and blocking the net , and winning the first game relatively smoothly at 25 : 18 .
the turkey team , which entered the second set , played fiercely and led by 6 : 2 at the beginning . the chinese team asked for a break and adjusted its form . the chinese team gradually chased the score to 7 : 00 and then repeatedly stopped scoring 7 : 0 . the turkish team chased the score to 15 : 19 at the end of the game . the chinese team chased the 2 : 2 company after winning the 24 : 20 .
the situation in the third set was very sticky , with the score rising alternately to 19 .
the turkey team made a mistake at the crucial moment . after the chinese team took the lead by 21 : 19 , it also won the 24 : 21 match with zhu ting 's strong deduction and Zhang changning 's attack . the turkish team then chased the score to 23 : 24 . after the chinese team requested a suspension , Zhang changning scored the offensive goal , and the chinese team locked the victory by 25 : 23 .
Chinese women &apos;s volleyball coach Lang Ping admitted after the game , the whole game is not easy .
&quot; we are better prepared , we have a good net , the Turkish team is more comprehensive , and we must reduce our mistakes and strive to win through our own initiative , &quot; he said .
Ju Ting , who played for Turkey &apos;s Wakiver Bank team in the face of a familiar teammate , was restricted in the first game of the day , then she took the initiative to change , and continued to play a strong offensive .
" we are very familiar with each other , and it is normal for the chinese team to keep an eye on each other , but the chinese team has played extremely well in intercepting the nets and attacking in case of miscommunication . "
China &apos;s women &apos;s volleyball team will be on a one @-@ day truce for physical and technical training , and on Oct. 2 will play Canada , the third opponent in the group match .
chinanews network hengshui , september 30 ( Cui zhiping , Wang peng ) on the 30th , Hebei hengshui high - tech zone held a concentrated opening ceremony for key projects in the second half of 2018 .
the six projects started on that day with a total investment of 4.29 billion yuan .
on that day , the Hengshui City Party Committee Standing Committee , Vice Mayor Yang Shikun announced the commencement of work .
according to Yao xinghui , director of the Hebei Hengshui high - tech district management committee , the six projects with a total investment of 4.29 - billion yuan started today are all industrial projects . they include the transformation and upgrading of traditional industries , as well as the cultivation and introduction of new industries , and cover many industries such as civil - military integration , cloud factories , food , medicine , and chemical industry . the projects have a high scientific and technological content , industrial levels , and the added value of products .
it is believed that the construction and commissioning of this batch of projects will inject a powerful driving force into the realization of the goal of " building a 100 - billion - yuan - grade industrial park and striving to create a national - level high - tech zone " in advance .
Yang shikun , member of the standing committee of the Hengshui city CPC committee and vice mayor , announced the start of the project .
Yao said that the region has successfully launched a series of major activities , including the china hengshui international life science summit and the great health industry development forum , the high - end equipment industry hengshui summit of academicians of the chinese academy of sciences , and the " double coordination " innovation forum between 2018 hengshui and Tianjin , to vigorously develop the three major strategic and emerging industries of new materials , energy , great health , and high - end equipment manufacturing .
the China @-@ US stem cell project will be officially launched by the end of the year .
China vanadium titanium system project 10,000 @-@ ton pilot base , the first domestic , the world &apos;s largest megawatt supercritical carbon dioxide compressor experimental platform began construction .
the advanced super computing center of hongan ( Hengshui ) , which ranks among the top 10 in the world , has been approved and built by provinces and cities .
Yao said that by the end of this year , the region will have completed 240,000 square meters of science and technology valley ii , including three research and development bases and exhibition centers for digital information , new energy materials , and life and health .
we will actively build the " chinese academy of science and technology + " innovation model " and the " one platform and one base of the two houses , " and promote the integration and innovation of scientific and technological achievements through multidisciplinary intersection , multi - unit cooperation , and multi - industry integration .
nearly 1,000 state - owned scenic spots cut ticket prices by more than 20 percent
&#91; abstract &#93; As of September 28 , 981 scenic spots ( 74 free @-@ of @-@ charge and 907 lower prices ) had been opened or announced to the public in various localities , while Shilin , Dali Santa , Yulong Xueshan , Guilin Li River in Guangxi , Wuyi Mountain in Fujian , Zhang Jiajie in Hunan , Terracotta warriors &apos; terracotta in Shaanxi , Sanqing Mountain in Jiangxi and Kanas in Xinjiang had all been reduced .
in order to implement the central economic work conference and the " government work report " policy decisions and arrangements , the state development and reform commission issued on 28 june the " guidance on perfecting the ticket price formation mechanism for state - owned scenic spots to reduce ticket prices for key state - owned scenic spots " ( hereinafter referred to as the guidance ) , calling for perfecting the ticket price formation mechanism for state - owned scenic spots in terms of rationally defining the cost composition of ticket pricing , innovating the way of price management , and strictly carrying out the pricing procedures , so as to ensure that the key state - owned scenic spots with high prices will achieve marked results by the end of september .
all localities have actively carried out work in accordance with the requirements for deployment , and have successively lowered the ticket prices for a number of key state - owned scenic spots .
as of 28 september , various localities had promulgated measures to open or reduce prices for 981 scenic spots ( 74 free and 907 reduced ) , of which 159 were scenic spots at level 5A and 534 were scenic spots at level 4A , making a total of 693 , or 70.6 percent .
of the 907 scenic spots , 491 , or 54.3 per cent , fell by more than 20 per cent or 214 , or 23.6 per cent , by more than 30 per cent .
Yunnan , Shandong , Guangxi , Shaanxi and other provinces reduced the number of scenic spots more , among which Yunnan reduced the number of scenic spots more than 100 , an overall decline of more than 30 per cent .
Anhui , Chongqing and other eight provinces ( districts , municipalities ) government pricing level 5A scenic spots to achieve price reductions .
Yunnan 's shilin , Dali 's three towers , yulong xueshan , Guangxi 's Guilin li river , Fujian 's Wuyi mountain , Hunan 's zhangjiajie , Shaanxi 's terracotta warriors and horses , Jiangxi 's sanqing mountain , and Xinjiang 's Kanas , all have all implemented price reductions .
the gradual return of ticket prices to reasonable ranges in key state - owned scenic areas will be conducive to accelerating the transformation of the tourism industry from a ticket economy to an industrial economy , from small - scale tourism to mass tourism , and from scenic spots to whole - region tourism , to forming a benign circle of optimizing the supply structure of the tourism industry and steadily expanding the demand for tourism consumption , and to promoting the sustained and healthy development of the scenic areas and the tourism industry .
at the same time , the state development and reform commission stressed that all localities should strengthen the regulation of price order in scenic spots , guide scenic spots to upgrade their services , and ensure that prices are not lowered .
in addition , the state development and reform commission has carried out special inspections of the recent media reports that the ticket prices in some scenic spots have dropped too little and that the prices have not decreased in real terms . the state development and reform commission has urged all localities to deal with the matter seriously , promptly respond to the concerns of the society , and earnestly put the price reduction into effect .
HKTDC conducts short- , medium- and long @-@ term optimization work in an orderly manner
the Macao Trade and Investment Promotion Bureau has submitted reports on the short- , medium- and long @-@ term optimization of the work on &quot; major investment migrants &quot; and &quot; skilled migrants . &quot; in addition to stepping up the promotion and implementation of the work contained in the reports , the Macao Trade and Investment Promotion Bureau has been constantly listening to public opinions and continuously optimizing the contents of the reports and related work .
the TDC will brief various sectors of the community on the relevant optimization work as soon as possible .
of these , five are short @-@ term measures implemented within this year ; five are medium @-@ term measures implemented within 2019 ; and one is long @-@ term measures .
in accordance with the instructions given by the economic and financial secretary , mr andrew Leung , the TDC also conducted a comprehensive review of its internal management system .
the five short - term measures introduced this year include :
1 . carry out follow @-@ up work . give priority to cases which are about to expire for seven years , those mentioned in the ICAC report and those which have been renewed . if there is evidence of misconduct or breach of the law , the case will be referred to the relevant judicial authorities for follow @-@ up action ;
2 . on @-@ site inspections of projects involving &quot; major investment migrants . &quot; by late September , more than 20 investment projects had been inspected ;
3 . to conduct a comprehensive review of the current assessment system . the six principles for the analysis of investment projects have been reformulated in assessing applications for &quot; major investment migrants . &quot; in assessing applications for &quot; technical migrants , &quot; the examination and approval mechanism will be improved by clearly defining the elements conducive to the development of the Macao Special Administrative Region and the conditions for preferential recruitment of talent . a list of &quot; ten types of jobs in five industries &quot; has also been drawn up to tie in with the administrative direction of the HKSAR Government ;
4 . increasing transparency of information , including plans to gradually promulgate the approval criteria , grading criteria and weights , and to further refine and make public the approval data from the fourth quarter of this year ;
5 . with regard to the refinement of the validation mechanism , prior verification of work in Australia has been required ; significant investments are required to be audited on @-@ site and financial statements submitted .
the five medium @-@ term measures implemented in 2019 include :
1 . setting up a mechanism to listen regularly to the views of the Talent Development Committee and the Economic Development Committee . a working meeting was held with the Economic Development Committee in September to discuss the establishment of such a mechanism .
2 . requires the applicant to submit an annual financial statement prepared by an independent third party in order to keep the operation of the investment project under review ;
3 . further standardize and electronic the processing of case applications and approvals in order to reduce human error ;
4 . a comprehensive review of the current staffing establishment to facilitate the implementation of a number of optimization measures ;
5 . intensifying the study on the revision of the Temporary Residence System for Investors , Managers and Specially Qualified Technicians .
with regard to long @-@ term measures , it is expected that the drafting of the relevant legislation will commence in the first half of 2019 , with a view to completing it as soon as possible , further clarifying the criteria for approving temporary residence permits , the review mechanism and the confirmation mechanism , and adding an investigation function to the TDC in order to more accurately examine and supervise applications for temporary residence permits .
experts from china 's film - free cotton field observation and discussion activities walked into the experimental fields and listened to a briefing by a representative of the chinese academy of engineering 's yu shuxun academician team .
Xinhua news agency , shaya , Xinjiang , september 30 ( Geng dandan Wang xiaojun ) - the experimental base for the cultivation of non-membrane cotton in shaya county , Xinjiang , has been enjoying a happy growth . compared with the ground - film cotton nearby , " it is no less beautiful " and clusters of snow - white cotton are competing to " open up " and are full of branches .
from 27 to 28 september , the national on - site observation and discussion and exchange activities on film - free cotton were held in Saya county , Xinjiang .
at the meeting , the reporter learned that the membrane - free cotton technology system , with " china cotton 619 " as the main body and its supporting cultivation measures , has preliminarily realized the goal of no - film cultivation in cotton fields , reduced the pollution of the ecological environment and raw cotton by the residue of Xinjiang cotton fields , and made great progress in the study and demonstration of comprehensive cotton - free cotton technology .
Yu shuxun , academician of the chinese academy of engineering , noted cotton genetic breeder , and chief scientist of the national modern agricultural technology system , briefed Zhou guomao , secretary of the party committee of Zhejiang university of agriculture and forestry , on the growth of film - free cotton .
" the comprehensive technology we have developed for cotton without film can completely realize cotton cultivation without film , can completely solve the problem of pollution caused by residual film , and can realize green cotton planting . "
Yu shuxun , academician of the chinese academy of engineering .
Xinjiang is the most important cotton @-@ producing region in China , with 35 million mu of cotton planted in 2017 , accounting for 61 per cent of the country &apos;s cotton area , according to the National Bureau of Statistics .
since the introduction of the land film into china in 1982 , all kinds of crops in Xinjiang have covered an area of more than 50 million mu and used about 300,000 tons of land film annually .
among them , the coverage rate of cotton film reaches 100 % , and the coated cotton field accounts for about 60 % of Xinjiang film usage .
the production of film - less cotton can be measured and the yield of cotton can be 320 kg to 350 kg per mu .
with the increasing input of Xinjiang film , the low recovery rate of residual film , the increasing amount of residue in soil and the destruction of soil structure caused by residue film have seriously affected the sustainable development of agriculture .
residues not only cause serious soil pollution , but also have a great impact on cotton fiber quality .
at present , more than one - third of Xinjiang 's cotton fields have been mechanized .
in 2017 , Xinjiang will have an area of about 14 million mu of mechanized cotton .
in the course of harvesting machine - made cotton , it is difficult to remove the shredded film from the surface of a large number of cotton plants and the shredded film doped in raw cotton during the processing of raw cotton , nor can it be completely removed during the subsequent processing of textile products , seriously affecting the quality of textile products .
on 28 september , a nationwide on - the - spot observation and discussion and exchange activity on film - free cotton was held in Sayya county , Xinjiang .
Yu shuxun led his team through eight years to implement the " china cotton 619 " film - free cotton technology to " add wings " to Xinjiang 's agricultural green development in an effort to tackle the pollution of cotton fields , simplify cotton planting technology , and improve cotton field efficiency .
Yu shuxun introduced that through innovative breeding methods , a new strain of land - based cotton , " middle cotton 619 , " which is particularly precocious , salt - resistant , low temperature - resistant , and abundant , has been developed .
" under the condition of no - film cultivation in southern Xinjiang , the " middle cotton 619 " has realized a series of supporting measures , such as mechanical support for no - film seeding , improvement in seeding depth , shallow burial of drip tubes under no - film conditions , suitable screening for seeding density , and rational chemical control . "
at present , demonstration bases for film - free cotton have been set up in Aksu , Kurl , Alar , and other places , with a yield of 4,800 kg per hectare .
film - free cotton cultivation , achieve bumper production , cost - saving , environmental protection , comprehensive benefits .
Zhang donghai , an agronomist at the agricultural institute of the third division of the Xinjiang production and construction corps , said : through the research and demonstration of membrane - free cotton cultivation technology in the past six years , the output of cotton seeds without film can completely realize 320 kg to 350 kg per mu , or even higher .
&quot; the promotion of film @-@ free cotton cultivation technology is very promising . &quot;
Zhang donghai believes that at present , membrane - free cotton cultivation technology can completely solve the problem of soil residue pollution , but there is still a certain gap between the economic benefits and the land film cultivation .
" the support of cotton purchase prices will be conducive to future popularization . "
Yu shuxun said : in the next step , he and his team will continue to carry out in - depth study and widespread application of film - free cotton , make the industry of film - free cotton stronger , and thoroughly solve the problem of soil pollution caused by the earth 's film .
Guangdong navy , air force respond positively to national day golden week transportation - china new zealand network
on 29 September , the seventh day of the commissioning of the Hong Kong section of the High Speed Railway and the first weekend of its opening , the West Kowloon Station was crowded with people .
as the national day golden week ( 1 - 7 october ) is approaching , this reporter has learned from relevant departments in the past few days that Guangdong railway , air , water , highway , and other transportation departments have actively planned and increased transportation capacity , promulgated various safeguard measures , and made every effort to ensure the safe and orderly transportation of passengers within the borders during the golden week .
during this year 's national day golden week , the Guangzhou railway group is expected to carry 17.8 million passengers , an increase of 1.505 million , or 9.2 percent , over the same period last year , according to china railway Guangzhou bureau group limited ( " Guangzhou iron group " ) .
to meet passenger demand , the Guangzhou railway group plans to increase the number of high - speed trains by 104 and the speed trains by 85 , mainly focusing on popular lines such as beijing , Guangzhou , Shanghai , Shenzhen , and Hangzhou - Shenzhen high - speed railways .
Guangzhou baiyun airport may become the busiest airport in the mainland during this year 's national day golden week , with an estimated passenger throughput of over 1.4 million and more than 9,200 flights .
with more and more international routes , the airport expects a sharp increase in international passenger traffic to be a prominent feature of this year &apos;s Golden Week holiday .
it has been learned that Singapore , bangkok , Phuket island , Jakarta , colombo , Maldives , manila , and other places are all popular cities for this year 's national day holidays . tourism in Kathmandu , kuala Lumpur , Bali , and other popular places also continue to flourish , and some flights are " hard to get one ticket . "
some airlines have particularly increased their operations , such as Shenzhen Airlines adding one Guangzhou @-@ Hanoi flight per day , Iran &apos;s Mahan Airlines adding one Guangzhou @-@ Tehran flight per Saturday , and Vietnam &apos;s Vietnam @-@ Vietnam Airways adding one Guangzhou @-@ Hanoi flight per Tuesday and Thursday .
in order to do a good job in providing holiday support , Baiyun airport has strengthened its support for key posts , such as " seat allocation , " " baggage support , " " on - duty service , " " passenger security inspection , " and made preparations for the handling of large - scale flight delays .
according to china southern airlines , flights to australia , new zealand , north america , japan , and south korea on this year 's national day golden week are very hot , and flights to mainland china 's tourist destinations , such as Hainan , Chengdu , luzhou , jiuhua shan , Anshan , and huangshan , are also quite popular .
Southern Airways plans to add 50 flights during the Golden Week , including 10 flights to and from Chiang Mai in Guangzhou .
according to the Guangdong maritime administration , before the festival , it conducted a rigorous investigation on key vessels such as water tourist boats , passenger ferries in the qiongzhou strait , high - speed passenger boats in the pearl river estuary , and ferry boats to ensure the stability of the water traffic situation during the long holidays .
during the golden week , Guangdong province is expected to rank first in china in terms of traffic volume .
Guangdong traffic group recently issued a holiday highway travel guidelines , highway traffic is expected to grow by about 12 % .
the General Administration of Market Supervision recently issued the &quot; Notice on Strengthening Market Price Supervision during the Mid @-@ Autumn Festival National Day in 2018 , &quot; which calls for tightening supervision over housing rental and real estate prices , sternly rectifying collusion in rental prices , hoarding of rental housing sources , fabrication of false information to inflate rents , arbitrary collection of fees by means of bundling services , publication of misleading price information and failure to mark prices .
the circular made it clear that we should strengthen the early warning of price monitoring and pay close attention to market price developments .
all localities should pay close attention to the daily necessities of high - consumption grain , oil , meat , poultry , eggs , vegetable , milk , and salt , as well as the changes in the market and prices of local residents ' holiday consumer goods , and step up price monitoring and analysis and early warning .
once the trend of market fluctuation is discovered , the problem of seedling is solved in a timely manner and effective measures are taken .
it is necessary to strengthen supervision and inspection of the wholesale and retail links of daily necessities , increase the frequency of monitoring and supervision of places closely related to the daily consumption of the masses , such as the merchant supermarkets and the agricultural and trade markets , and urge operators to abide by the law and run honestly .
the circular points out that it is necessary to strengthen inspection in key areas , create a favorable environment for holiday consumption , strengthen the supervision and control of ticket prices in state - owned scenic areas , and lay stress on investigating and punishing illegal activities in state - owned scenic areas , such as failing to implement the price levels or floating ranges set by the government , arbitrarily setting up additional fee items , raising ticket prices in disguised form of setting up " garden " tickets in violation of regulations , setting up large price discounts , binding sales , failing to mark prices in accordance with regulations , failing to carry out preferential measures , raising prices in addition to impose compulsory charges , and other illegal charges .
the circular calls for tightening supervision over the prices of basic necessities , especially agricultural products .
affected by seasonal changes , natural disasters , and sudden epidemics , the prices of agricultural products essential to life , such as vegetables and pork , have recently fluctuated in some areas .
all localities should , in light of local conditions , conscientiously strengthen market price supervision of agricultural and sideline products , cooperate with relevant departments in stabilizing production and market supply , and organize forces to carry out key market inspections and random spot checks .
we will increase the frequency of inspection of pork and other commodities with tight supplies and relatively high prices , and severely investigate and deal with illegal activities such as hoarding , raising prices , and colluding in raising prices .
the circular points out that it is necessary to strengthen price supervision in the areas of housing rental and real estate .
all localities should pay close attention to the price behavior of real estate enterprises , intermediary companies , and enterprises related to housing rental , strictly check the collusion of rent prices , hoard rental housing sources , fabricate false speculation and make false information about rent hikes , arbitrarily collect fees by means of bundling services , publish misleading price information , fail to mark prices , and other price violations , and step up inspection of the situation in selling hot - selling properties and real estate intermediary prices .
the circular mentions that all localities should conscientiously supervise the prices of other links in the tourism industry , make efforts to standardize the price order of such links as catering , lodging , shopping , sightseeing , entertainment , and parking , guide business operators to do a good job in publicizing the prices of specific codes and charges , and severely investigate and deal with all kinds of illegal pricing activities .
the circular says that it is necessary to step up inspection of highway , railway , civil aviation , water transportation and other transportation prices , and severely investigate and deal with illegal activities such as illegally raising prices , collecting extra prices , and failing to mark prices according to regulations .
implement the policy of &quot; Green Channel &quot; for the transportation of fresh agricultural products and exemption of minibus tolls on major holidays .
it is necessary to innovate the means and methods of supervision and control , strengthen the publicity of price laws and regulations for online and offline commodity retail enterprises and e - commerce platforms , urge operators to improve price promotion plans , and investigate and deal with such illegal activities as fictitious original prices , misleading price labels , and failure to fulfill price commitments according to law .
a total of 1.7 million passengers have been transported to and from Shanghai and hong kong since the 15 th anniversary of the Shanghai - hong kong train last week .
at the same time , passengers from hong kong and Macau will be allowed to pass customs clearance for no more than 15 seconds .
on 1 october 2003 , the state council approved the establishment of a temporary Shanghai - Kowloon express train port , and the Shanghai railway port is china 's first long - distance railway passenger port , marking the opening of Shanghai to the outside world with " three wings flying side by side " for water transport , aviation , and land .
up to now , Shanghai - hong kong train has been in operation for 15 years .
Shanghai - hong kong railway border inspection , which is charged with the task of crossing the border between Shanghai and hong kong , revealed on the 1 st that since the opening of the Shanghai - hong kong railway , the speed of trains in Shanghai and hong kong has been raised three times , and the one - way journey time has been shortened from the previous 30 hours to 19 hours ; the annual passenger flow has increased from less than 80,000 to more than 150,000 ; and in the past 15 years , the total number of passengers carrying passengers to and leaving Shanghai and hong kong has surpassed 1.7 million .
it has been learned that over the past 15 years , the Shanghai railway frontier inspection station and the Shanghai - Kowloon train station have signed a police coordination mechanism and dispatched police officers to carry out on - board supervision and control , thus realizing a total service and control coverage of 1,991 km .
in the past 15 years , the Shanghai railway border control station has cracked down on nearly 1,000 cases of various kinds of illegal and illegal activities , successfully cracking down on the cases of foreigners smuggling into china with false certificates and using others ' documents to replace them .
the station has also set up a work - to - work exchange mechanism with the JIU units , conducted regular drills of the railway port 's comprehensive anti - terrorism department , and joined forces to build a " three - level moat protection belt " at the railway port .
it has been learned that in the past 15 years , the Shanghai railway frontier inspection department has constantly innovated in service , and the speed of customs clearance has greatly increased .
the border post also set up a &quot; Jinglan &quot; volunteer service to provide loving help to the elderly , pregnant women and passengers carrying babies .
the reporter learned from the ministry of finance on the 30th that in order to further encourage foreign investors to invest in china , the four departments of the ministry of finance , the state administration of taxation , the state development and reform commission , and the ministry of commerce recently jointly issued a circular to extend the scope of application of the policy of withholding advance income tax from domestic direct investment to all projects and fields not prohibited from foreign investment .
this policy has been implemented since 1 January 2018 .
the circular makes it clear that the direct investment made by foreign investors with their share of profits includes the behavior of foreign investors with their share of profits in such equity investments as capital increase , new construction , and equity acquisition , but does not include the addition , transfer , or acquisition of shares of listed companies other than those that qualify for strategic investment .
if an overseas investor can enjoy the policy of withholding advance income tax for the time being , but does not actually enjoy it , he or she may , within three years from the date of actual payment of the relevant tax , apply for retroactive enjoyment of the policy and return the tax already paid .
in addition , after overseas investors enjoy the stipulated treatment of withholding advance income tax for the time being , those enterprises that meet the conditions for special reorganization and actually carry out tax treatment according to special reorganization may continue to enjoy the treatment of withholding advance income tax for the time being .
in order to ensure that the profits obtained by foreign investors are actually used for direct investment , the circular stipulates that if the profits used by foreign investors for direct investment are paid in cash , the relevant funds will be transferred directly from the account of the profit distribution enterprise to the account of the invested enterprise or the equity transferor , and the profits used by foreign investors for direct investment will not be turned around in other accounts inside or outside the country before direct investment .
the circular also requires tax authorities to strengthen follow @-@ up management in accordance with the law .
foreign investors have already enjoyed the policy of temporarily not levying pre - mentioned income tax . those who fail to meet the prescribed conditions after subsequent management and verification by the tax departments are regarded as foreign investors who have failed to file and pay enterprise income tax in accordance with the stipulations , and will be investigated according to law for the delayed payment of taxes , which will be calculated from the date when the relevant profits are paid .
the Food and Drug Administration ( FDA ) said Friday it would not allow imports of raw materials and preparations made with the company &apos;s raw materials from the Chinese pharmaceutical industry .
a drug previously produced by the Hua Hai pharmaceutical industry was recalled for containing a possible carcinogen .
the European Medical Agency said it was considering further action on other components of the plant &apos;s production .
the FDA said it found major production process problems during an FDA inspection of pharmaceutical plants in China &apos;s maritime industry and stopped importing them .
the FDA also said it would ban imports until the industry discovered how the impurities were produced and improved its quality @-@ control system .
" the company is taking positive and forceful measures to rectify the problems in this us - european official inspection , and is very surprised and regretful about the way the us - european official handling and handling of the matter has been handled , " the Huahai pharmaceutical industry said in a statement on its website on 29 september .
in the current complex market environment , the company is worried about this .
at present , the company is organizing teams , including professional lawyers , to communicate and lodge complaints with us and eu officials in accordance with relevant procedures in order to resume production as soon as possible . "
Shanghai ( Reuters ) - China Securities Regulatory Commission ( CSRC ) announced Friday night that the CSRC approved the initial application for China People &apos;s Insurance Group Co . , Ltd. in accordance with legal procedures .
but the SFC &apos;s official Weixin Public did not disclose the size of the IPO .
China People &apos;s Insurance Corp. submitted an application to the China Securities Regulatory Commission on Sept . 29 last year to issue up to 4.599 billion A @-@ shares and plan to list them on the Shanghai Stock Exchange .
according to prior disclosures published by the securities regulatory commission , the number of companies applying to issue new shares this time does not exceed 9.78 percent of the total share capital after listing , and does not include any shares that may be issued under the overallotment option .
the money raised will be used to replenish the company &apos;s capital .
on 9 april this year , the securities regulatory commission announced the prospectus of the chinese people 's insurance company ( draft declaration ) .
the prospectus shows that prior to the issuance of A shares , China People &apos;s Insurance Corporation had a total share capital of 42.424 billion shares . assuming that the A shares of 4.599 billion shares were issued without exercising the option of overallotment , A shares would not exceed 47.023 billion shares , of which A shares would not exceed 38.296 billion shares and H shares would be 8.726 billion shares .
June 5 China People &apos;s Insurance IPO application through the Development Committee .
as at 31 December 2017 , the Ministry of Finance held 70.47 per cent of the total equity of China People &apos;s Insurance Corporation and the Social Security Fund held 10.2 per cent .
after China &apos;s A @-@ share issue , the Treasury &apos;s stake will be diluted to 63.58 % , and the Social Security Fund &apos;s stake will be 9.2 % .
as of Friday , China People &apos;s Insurance Corporation &apos;s H @-@ shares closed at HK $ 3.52 , up 1.44 % that day .
