therefore , the north control side indicated that it would reserve the right to pursue the responsibility of the parties concerned by all means .
the agricultural development bank of china will invest 20 billion yuan to support the purchase of Jilin Qiu grain .
since September , crops across Jilin Province have been experiencing harvest peaks .
this reporter learned from the Jilin provincial branch of the china agricultural development bank that at present , the amount of credit funds available for agricultural issuance has reached 20 billion yuan to ensure adequate supply of Jilin autumn grain purchase funds .
it has been learned that this year the grain production situation in Jilin is generally stable , and some grain processing enterprises have increased their production capacity , the opening rate has risen , and the demand for grain has increased .
in order to ensure the supply of funds for grain policy acquisition , agricultural distribution has actively carried out the autumn grain purchase of silver enterprises through visits to peasant households , processing enterprises , trading enterprises , and other types of purchasing entities .
at present , agricultural distribution has invested 5.2 billion yuan to support the purchase of 11.58 billion jin of autumn grain by various grain purchasing bodies .
there are already 120 major grain purchasing entities in Jilin province with nearly 300 purchase points , ensuring that the main grain producing counties are " fully covered " and leaving no " blank spots " for purchasing funds .
according to the relevant responsible person of the agricultural issue , according to the progress of the purchase and the demand for enterprise funds , if there is a shortage of funds for the purchase , the agricultural issue will apply for additional funds on the basis of 20 - billion yuan of credit funds to ensure the timely and full supply of funds , maintain stability in the grain market , and protect the interests of peasants .
Chinese journalists were taken away by police at the annual meeting of the British Conservative Party , and China demanded an apology
according to the website of the chinese embassy in britain , a spokesman for the embassy in britain answered a reporter 's question on the 1 st about a chinese reporter being taken away by the police during the annual meeting of the british conservatives .
the spokesman pointed out : we demand that the Tory human rights commission stop interfering in china 's internal affairs , stop interfering in hong kong affairs , and ask the organizers of the meeting to apologize to chinese reporters .
a reporter asked : during the annual meeting of the british conservative party on 30 september , the party 's human rights committee held a side event on the hong kong issue and invited the hong kong opposition to speak at the meeting .
a Chinese journalist was taken away by the police during the event .
do you have any comment ?
in response , the spokesman said that in the 21 years since hong kong 's return to the motherland , the practice of " one country , two systems " had been extremely successful , and hong kong 's development achievements were universally acknowledged .
Hong kong is china 's hong kong , and hong kong affairs are purely china 's internal affairs .
the Conservative Party Human Rights Committee used the party &apos;s annual meeting to hold a side event to promote anti @-@ China separatist forces . the Chinese side expressed grave concern and strong dissatisfaction .
we are firmly opposed to interference in hong kong affairs by any organization in any way .
any attempt or action to advocate " hong kong independence " will be futile .
the spokesman said that britain has always proclaimed freedom of speech , but it is totally unacceptable that chinese journalists , when asked to express their views at the side meetings , have been obstructed in every way and even physically assaulted .
we demand that the Conservative Human Rights Commission stop interfering in China &apos;s internal affairs , stop meddling in Hong Kong affairs , and ask the organizers of the conference to apologize to Chinese journalists .
the fifth world internet congress will be held in Wuzhen , Zhejiang province , from 7 to 9 november , and the world internet will soon enter Wuzhen time again .
as a global Internet congregation , the World Internet Congress has received a high degree of attention and wide recognition in the global Internet field .
over the past five years , the world internet congress has set up a large stage for the exchange of advanced technologies on the internet , and the wide application of technological achievements at the conference has added new impetus to global economic development .
results Release Converts World Internet Frontiers
in the area of the Internet , what are the world &apos;s top @-@ notch and most visible achievements ?
the leading scientific and technological results released at the World Internet Congress provide the answer .
the third world internet conference released for the first time 15 leading scientific and technological achievements .
the results of the exhibition were innovative , applied in a wide range of fields , and played a big role in stimulating radiation . they reflected the latest and most important breakthroughs in science and technology in the world 's internet field at that time , and reflected the speed and future prospects of the development of the network information field .
optical Quantum Computers , 5G , Artificial Intelligence capable of computing emotions , and so on , the results released at the Fourth World Internet Congress are even more dazzling .
the conference organizing committee set up a special committee to recommend the world 's leading scientific and technological achievements in the internet . composed of 44 well - known experts and scholars from 10 countries , including china and the united states , the committee collected nearly 1,000 innovative achievements in the internet field from all over the world , and finally evaluated 18 representative achievements , including the " huawei 3GPP 5G pre - commercial system " " " Arm security structure " " Microsoft 's " mini - ice " " " BeiDou satellite navigation system " based on the " shenwei lake taiguang computer super-light " supersystem .
currently , more than 50 countries and regions are covered by the Beidou satellite navigation system , involving more than 3 billion people .
the supercomputer Shenwei Taihu Light completed more than 2 million operational tasks and supported more than 100 applications .
the Microsoft Little Ice , pioneered by Microsoft &apos;s China research and development team , has set out from China and has now landed in China , Japan , the United States , India , Indonesia and other countries , serving as a host to television programs , radio hosts and singers . China &apos;s Internet technology development has frequently flashed to the forefront of the world &apos;s science and technology camp , attracting surprises from all over the world , becoming a gathering place and a vane for the world &apos;s top Internet technologies .
new platform for technology exchange at &quot; Internet Light &quot; Expo
as one of the important contents of the world internet congress , the " light of the internet " expo drives the interactive exchange of the global achievements in internet science , technology , and innovation , and provides an important platform for internet enterprises to showcase their latest achievements .
the " light of the internet " expo showcases new achievements , new technologies , and applications of the internet worldwide . it has different thematic exhibition areas and functional sections . it selects globally renowned internet enterprises and innovative enterprises according to different scientific and technological categories . it gathers cutting - edge achievements , displays innovative technologies , and embodies the light of civilization , the light of the future , and the light of the world in internet exchanges .
taking the " internet light " expo of the fourth world internet congress as an example , the expo attracts 411 well - known domestic and foreign enterprises from all over the world to participate in the expo . its products cover the latest achievements in the development of global internet technology and applications , such as cloud computing , things networking , artificial intelligence , and the digital economy , and highlight the characteristics of global vision , innovation - driven , and open cooperation .
more than 110 new product technology launches and 10 internet project collaboration sessions were held during the conference , providing a broad arena for global digital economic cooperation .
a paper @-@ based examination paper , scanned by a mobile phone or tablet computer , can immediately identify the contents and make corrections ; a half @-@ meter @-@ high unmanned car carrying goods can independently complete rapid delivery ; and with the owner &apos;s voice commands alone , intelligent homes can realize voice shopping , cell phone recharge , take @-@ away sales , music play , and a centralized appearance of top @-@ notch Internet science and technology achievements at the Internet Expo , which has become a new platform for exchanges between the global technology industry and the Internet .
achievements in Internet science and technology for the benefit of all peoples
the innovative development driven by internet technology is ultimately to create a better future for the people of all countries in the world and to create a more equitable , open , and inclusive environment for the happiness of mankind , economic development , and social well - being .
in China , an Internet power with a huge user base , Internet technology has a strong amplification effect in specific applications .
for example , China &apos;s BeiDou provides users with high @-@ precision and reliable positioning , speed @-@ measuring and timing services , as well as unique short @-@ message communication capabilities . the rapid development of artificial intelligence technology has reconfigured functions for traditional industries and promoted industrial progress . it has played a positive role in many fields , such as finance , transportation , health and safety .
according to the 42 nd " statistical report on china 's internet development " released by the china internet information center , china , as the largest internet market in the world , is promoting social development and progress in the process of digitalization .
and the dividends of Internet technology development are by no means limited to China , and its achievements have also brought a powerful driving force for the development of the entire world Internet and even the economy and society .
for example , china 's cross - border electric merchants and sharing economy are moving overseas , and this is increasingly supporting world economic growth . China 's new generation of information technology , such as cloud computing , big data , internet of things , and mobile internet , is speeding up the deepening of the global industrial division of labor , economic restructuring , and reshaping the pattern of global economic competition .
as outlined in the " Wuzhen initiative " released at the second world internet conference , sharing the fruits of network development and promoting the early formation of a network market connected to the world and creating more job opportunities will provide strong support for the sustained and healthy development of the global economy and enable more countries and people to take advantage of the fast train of the information age .
Lu Liang is known as the &quot; grocery kingdom . &quot;
from 30 september to 7 october , the second lu Liang special and superior functional food exhibition and the first farmers ' harvest festival were held in fenyang city , luiliang , Shanxi .
during the event , officials from lu Liang 's quarry area , fenyang city , jiacheng county , lanxian county , and other places invited tourists to experience the beauty of the countryside and jointly celebrate the farmers ' harvest festival through on - the - spot promotion .
on the eve of the national day , during the autumn harvest season , the city of lu Liang , known as the " grocery kingdom , " held a " grocery gathering , " in which more than 200 merchants took part in the display and sale of 426 types of excellent functional foods .
Lu Liang 's potato production ranks at the forefront in Shanxi . as one of the main production areas , lanxian county has in recent years extended its industrial chain through the development of potato production . while developing its industries , lanxian has also pushed villagers out of poverty . on the spot , the exhibitors introduced the new method of eating potatoes through the " potato feast " dish display . the businessmen from linxian county brought in fresh dates , green beans , peas , and millet .
Lu Liang agriculture has a long history , cereal cultivation began in Neolithic times , soybeans , soybeans , naked oats , millet , etc. have a history of four or five thousand years , red dates can be traced back to the Western Han Dynasty .
unique climate and diverse geomorphology , the formation of Lu Liang many characteristics of agricultural products , is a well @-@ known red dates , walnuts , small miscellaneous grains , fragrant liquor production base .
at present , luLiang city has preliminarily formed counties with the characteristics of linxian , Liulin red dates , fenyang , Zhongyang walnut , lanxian potato , xingxian county small grain , fangshan chinese herbs , Jiaotou edible fungus , filial piety facilities vegetables , brushes , and shilou honey . it has certified 1.6 million mu of pollution - free green organic products and 172 products .
more than 200 businesses took part in the exhibition with 426 specialties .
Li zhengyin , vice chairman of the Shanxi provincial committee of the chinese people 's political consultative conference and secretary of the lu Liang city CPC committee , said : the city will further open its agriculture to the outside world , promote production and marketing , and push lu Liang 's more excellent functional foods toward the whole country and the world .
in addition to gardening melons and fruits , pine farmers tasty , the beauty of the country also lies in the eco @-@ country tour , real @-@ life performance .
during the event , officials from the quarry area , Fenyang city , Jiaicheng county , lanxian county , and other places introduced local scenic spots to the participants , and invited tourists to visit the city .
Li huiyi , vice mayor of fenyang city , introduced that in fenyang ancient times there were general Di Qing of the song dynasty , and today there are well - known directors jia zhangke . in addition to popular folk culture such as fenzhou 's yangge and jinzhou 's " fenfen no drama , " there are tourist attractions such as " china 's xingfa village , the rejuvenation of jia Zhuang village , ecological sacred land ancient wuwen lake , beachuangxia 's upper forest , and summer resort river . "
the implementation of the rural rejuvenation strategy and the promotion of agricultural supply @-@ side reform are the means for Lu Liang to help the poor in the particularly difficult areas .
Li zhengyin frankly said that winning the battle to get rid of poverty and tackle the tough battle to help the poor is a very important way to help the people in impoverished areas lift themselves out of poverty and increase their incomes . " we sincerely hope that friends from all walks of life will " buy products from impoverished areas and offer love for helping the poor . "
with the theme of " celebrating bumper harvests , promoting culture , and rejuvenating the countryside , " the purpose of the event is to invite tourists to " display and sell characteristic mountain treasures , appreciate folk culture , and tour lu Liang meijing " and to build a number of famous agricultural products and food brands with a high reputation and market competitiveness , such as " lu Liang walnut " .
during the event , business attraction and trade contracts will also be held , and awards will be given to the " 10 best cultivators " " 10 best leaders for getting rich " " 10 best leaders for rural electric businessmen " and " 10 best chefs " .
the Xiamen city people 's government recently issued a circular that , starting from 1 october , migrant workers who hold the five consecutive years of Xiamen city residence permit , who have gone through employment registration procedures in Xiamen city and participated in the fifth consecutive year of social endowment insurance , and who have the " Xiamen city land and housing rights certificate " in Xiamen , may move in their accounts .
residents who have registered for employment in Xiamen city and who have participated in the fifth consecutive anniversary of the completion of Xiamen city social endowment insurance have the right to own the " Xiamen city land and housing rights certificate " in the ximing district and the huli district , and who have completed the fifth anniversary of their registration in Xiamen city , may move the registration into the xiamen district and the huli district .
at present , Xiamen city has six municipal districts , divided into the island 's Siming district and lakes district , and the offshore sea area , the catchment area , the tongan district , and the xiangan district .
this is the first time since August 2010 that Xiamen has relaxed the conditions within Xiamen Island .
Xinhua news agency , Fuzhou , october 1 ( reporter tai xiaoan ) on october 1 , the " regulations on the safety management of high - speed railways in Fujian province " officially came into effect .
according to the regulations , it is prohibited to lift kites , balloons , lanterns , aircraft , and other airborne objects and small aircraft within 500 meters on each side of the high - speed railway power line .
it stipulates that , on the basis of the " PRC law on railways , " the " regulations on railway safety management , " and other superior laws , and in light of Fujian 's geographical and climatic characteristics , supplementary provisions should be made to prohibit and restrict acts that affect the safety of high - speed railways , regulate construction and tree planting along high - speed railways , further clarify the subjects and scope of supervision and control of high - speed railways , and clearly define the duties and legal liabilities of law enforcement and supervision .
the regulations stipulate that in view of the fact that the coastal areas of Fujian province are prone to high winds , and light construction materials and light objects along high - speed railways are blown into high - speed railways , it is prohibited to lift kites , balloons , kong ming lamps , power umbrellas , aircraft , and other airborne objects within 500 meters of each side of the high - speed railroad power line conductor .
in addition , the owners or users of light objects such as plastic sheds , colored steel plates , and sunscreens along high - speed railway lines , as well as light floating objects such as low - altitude floating objects and plastic protective films produced during construction , shall take reinforcing and protective measures to prevent endangering the safety of high - speed railways .
in view of the fact that Fujian is located in hilly areas and has a large number of high - speed railway tunnels , the regulations require the construction of mountain ponds , reservoirs , dikes , excavated rivers , trunk canals , and wells within 200 meters of each side of the central line above the high - speed railway tunnels , which may affect the safety of tunnels , the opinions of the railway construction units or railway transport enterprises should be solicited .
at the same time , those responsible for violating the " regulations " will be ordered by the public security organs to make corrections ; in more serious cases , the unit will be fined between 5,000 yuan and 10,000 yuan , and the individual will be fined between 200 yuan and 500 yuan ; in serious cases , the unit will be fined between 10,000 yuan and 30,000 yuan , and the individual will be fined between 500 yuan and 1,000 yuan .
those who cause losses shall bear the liability for compensation according to law .
it has been learned that with the rapid development of railway construction , the mileage of high - speed railways with speeds of 200 km / h and above in Fujian province has now reached 1,516 km / h , which has enabled the city to open up to the public , and it is expected that the railway lines with speeds of 200 km / h and above in Fujian will reach 2,150 km / h in the next five years .
the implementation of these regulations will standardize the safety management of high - speed railways in Fujian province , further implement the duties of local government departments , coordinate railway and local forces , make joint efforts to ensure the safety of high - speed railways , and improve the safety and control system of high - speed railways in Fujian province .
Hong KONG Nov 5 ( Reuters ) - China &apos;s largest beer producer , China Resources ( Holdings ) Ltd . ( 0291.HK ) , announced on Monday that it would buy Heineken / Hein.AS , China &apos;s six breweries on the mainland and all of Heinrich Hong Kong &apos;s issued shares at a total cost of about HK $ 2,355 million .
at the same time , the company signed a trademark licensing agreement with Heineken to authorize China Resources to use the Heineken trademark in mainland China , Hong Kong and Macau for the production , marketing , distribution and sale of licensed products for a period of 20 years , which will be renewed on the same terms and conditions for a period of 10 years at a time until the termination of the trademark licence agreement .
China Resources announced in August that its direct controlling shareholder , Hua Run Group Ltd . , had reached an equity partnership agreement with Xi Li of about HK $ 28.5 billion .
at the same time , china resources has entered into long - term strategic co - operation arrangements with Healthy , including the acquisition of its existing business in china , hong kong and Macau , and integration with its beer business in china .
the transaction is a further implementation of the cooperation agreement .
China Resources said the deal with Healthy provided the group with an important strategic , long @-@ term development and value @-@ added opportunity to expand into the high @-@ end beer market , and that the long @-@ term cooperative relationship thus established would be highly complementary .
China Resources Co. closed Friday at HK $ 28.85 , down nearly 4.5 % in the past month .
thousands or thousands killed in tsunami disaster : China @-@ Singapore Network
a 7.5 @-@ magnitude shallow earthquake hit Indonesia &apos;s Sulawesi Island on September 28 , triggering a 6 @-@ metre tsunami .
the National Disaster Response Department announced on 30 September that the death toll had risen to 832 , mainly in the capital , Palu , and in the neighbouring epicentre of Dungala territory .
Vice President Carla says as many as thousands of casualties remain uncounted in some of the affected areas .
a strong earthquake and tsunami in central Sulawesi province on the afternoon of september 28 in indonesia have killed 832 people .
2.4 million people affected by collapse of thousands of buildings
in the aftermath of the Palu disaster , thousands of buildings collapsed and many roads were broken , with an estimated 2.4 million people affected , authorities said .
a hotel on the local coast collapsed and only 24 guests fled safely , with an estimated 50 to 60 trapped in rubble . calls for help were heard from time to time , and rescue workers successfully rescued a young woman on September 30 .
the authorities were unable to remove the rubble using heavy machinery to ensure the safety of the trapped persons and the search and rescue process was slow .
a shopping mall in the city collapsed , and hundreds of residents rushed to the scene waiting for news from relatives and friends .
many residents use social networking platforms to send letters seeking separated relatives and friends .
on September 30 , local time , Indonesian central Sulawesi Baru city , a hotel collapsed , relief work began .
whereabouts of 10 000 foreigners awaiting rescue : report
authorities say about 10,000 people are waiting for help in the city of Palu , scattered over 50 locations .
it was learned that 71 foreigners were in Palu at the time of the earthquake , 66 of whom were temporarily known to be safe , including 21 Chinese citizens , the remaining two French , two Malaysian tourists and one South Korean .
the chinese embassy in indonesia is trying through various channels to find out and verify the situation of chinese citizens in the disaster - stricken areas , and has not yet received any reports of casualties among chinese citizens .
communications in Dungala district , near the epicenter of the quake , remained suspended and 11 people were reported dead , but no further details were available .
the scene showed serious damage to coastal areas and ports in Dungala district , with a large number of buildings being swept away and corpses scattered throughout the area . Red Cross rescue teams are now on their way to search and rescue there .
Indonesian president inspects disaster situation , says reconstruction work begins soon
roads in Palu and Dungala were severely damaged , and on 30 September , Palu airport was open only to aircraft carrying relief supplies , allowing relief supplies and personnel to arrive as soon as possible and taking away seriously injured persons .
a number of local hospitals are still without electricity and the injured are treated outdoors .
more than 10,000 people were admitted to shelters , and some feared the aftershock would not return home , preferring to spend the night outdoors .
following the collapse of a prison in Palu , which triggered the escape of hundreds of prisoners , more than 100 prisoners in Dungala County took advantage of the chaos caused by the earthquake to remain in detention , and prisoners set fire to disturbances in detention centres .
Indonesian President Joko , who visited Palu on 30 September , noted that it was very difficult to resolve a large number of problems in a short time , including the restoration of communications .
he appealed to the victims for patience and said the authorities would start reconstruction work as soon as possible .
on the other hand , the Indonesian Minister of Finance announced that the Government had allocated 560 billion Indonesian guilders for disaster relief .
confirmed human case of H5N6 avian influenza in Guangdong Province
the Health Bureau says one human case of H5N6 avian influenza has been confirmed in Guangdong Province , according to the latest notification from the mainland health authorities .
the Health Bureau urged residents to avoid contact with birds and pay attention to personal and food hygiene .
according to the data , the patient , a 22 - year - old man , is now living in baiyun district , Guangzhou city , Guangdong province . he developed fever and other symptoms on 25 september . he was admitted to hospital on 26 september and is now being treated in isolation in a hospital . his condition is very serious .
the patient had slaughtered and eaten live poultry before onset .
since April 2014 , there have been confirmed cases of H5N6 avian influenza in Sichuan , Guangdong , Yunnan , Hubei , Hunan , Anhui and Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Regions .
the Health Bureau will maintain close liaison with the health authorities of the country and neighbouring areas and the World Health Organization ( WHO ) to monitor the situation closely .
to prevent human infection with avian influenza , the Health Bureau calls attention to the following :
avoid contact with birds or their secretions and excreta ; wash hands immediately if in contact ;
do not buy or carry unquarantined birds ;
do not eat poultry meat , offal , blood products and eggs that are not thoroughly cooked ;
pay attention to personal hygiene and wash hands frequently ;
if you develop symptoms such as fever , cough and respiratory difficulties , wear a mask and seek medical attention as soon as possible . details of travel history and animal contact history should also be given to doctors .
