this reporter learned from the china national railways corporation that today the national railways are facing a peak of passengers during the national day holiday . it is estimated that 16.19 million passengers will be dispatched and 714 more passenger trains will be operated , of which 136 will be medium-and long - distance passenger trains of the cross - railway bureau and 578 will be operated by the railways bureau .
on 30 september , 13.108 million passengers were dispatched by railway across the country , an increase of 584,000 passengers , or 4.7 percent , over the same period last year , and railway transportation across the country was safe and orderly .
among them , the Shanghai bureau group company sent 2.56 million passengers , an increase of 8.2 percent over the same period last year ; the Guangzhou bureau group company sent 1.855 million passengers , an increase of 12.9 percent over the same period last year ; and the beijing bureau group company sent 1.283 million passengers , an increase of 1.2 percent over the same period last year .
on October 1 , the Guangzhou @-@ Shenzhen High Speed Railway is expected to deliver 300,000 passengers ( 55,000 crossings ) and 137 pairs of passenger trains ( 83 crossings ) . the Harcourt Railway is expected to deliver 28,000 passengers and 30 passenger trains .
