however , at present , flights to and from hong kong in Ningxia are not convenient . after making enquiries about the timetable of the train , Mr. song found that the first train could arrive at 7 : 03 am and connect the city 's transportation to the golden bauhinia square . the time was just right .
he exclaimed to reporters : &quot; the high @-@ speed railway is really convenient , fast and punctual ! &quot;
the 70 one - hour short - haul trains between south Guangzhou , north Shenzhen and Fukuda and west Kowloon have greatly facilitated the arrival of residents from the Guangdong , hong kong and Macau big bay regions .
upon his arrival in hong kong , mr Lau , who lives in Shenzhen , is preparing to meet his hong kong friends at the peak of central .
&quot; both the Mainland and Hong Kong are on holiday on National Day . we intend to challenge ourselves to see if we can walk 50 kilometres of Hong Kong Island Trail , &quot; Mr Lau said .
he explained that they would not have dared easily try such a long hike had it not been for the opening of the high @-@ speed railway , easy access and sufficient time .
