chinanews , Fuzhou , september 30 ( reporter long min ) the sixth meeting of the standing committee of the 13 th Fujian provincial people 's congress voted to pass the " regulations on promoting the building of ecological civilization in Fujian province " on the 30 th .
green Water Castle Peak is Jinshan Yinshan is written into Fujian Province &apos;s legislation for the first time , running through the entire regulation and becoming an operational and enforceable provision .
Fujian is the first national ecological civilization test area in China .
according to a responsible person of the legal affairs office of the people 's government of Fujian province , it is necessary and urgent to form a basic law and regulations for the construction of ecological civilization based on the whole and the overall situation , so as to solve the problem of relying solely on scattered laws and regulations and policy documents to regulate and control the building of ecological civilization , and also to provide a legal basis for formulating relevant regulations , normative documents , and measures .
the regulations fully reflect Fujian 's characteristics and transform the practice of mature experience in the construction of ecological civilization into the form of laws and regulations to popularize it : for example , the " changting experience " formed in the work of soil and water conservation in Fujian should be summed up and promoted , and the local people 's governments at and above the county level should strengthen their unified leadership over soil and water conservation work .
the regulations stipulate that liability for damage to the ecological environment shall be investigated for life .
those who violate the requirements of scientific development and cause serious damage to the ecological environment and resources shall be held accountable for their leading cadres and responsible persons concerned for life .
it has been learned that the " regulations on promoting the building of ecological civilization in Fujian province " will come into force on 1 november this year .
China , Pakistan agree to complete economic corridor construction project in time to speed up Gwadar port construction
China and Pakistan have agreed to further consolidate and expand their economic ties , the foreign ministry said Sunday .
China and Pakistan issued a joint statement Sunday to further strengthen their strategic partnership .
the two sides reiterated their &quot; commitment to the construction of the China @-@ Pakistan economic corridor &quot; and &quot; opposition to negative propaganda against the China @-@ Pakistan economic corridor . &quot;
Reuters quoted the chinese foreign ministry as saying that china and Pakistan will " strengthen practical cooperation in the areas of trade and investment and enhance Pakistan 's industrial capacity through the establishment of joint ventures in priority areas , the transfer of labor - intensive industries , and the development of small and medium - sized enterprise cooperation . "
according to a press release published on the foreign ministry 's website , the two sides agreed to complete the construction of the sino - Pakistani economic corridor in a timely manner , speed up the construction of the port of Gwadar and supporting projects , focus on economic and social development , create jobs and improve people 's livelihood , and speed up cooperation in industry , parks , and agriculture .
" the two sides also agreed to complete the second phase of the Sino - Pakistani FTA negotiations as soon as possible and to continue to push forward the Sino - Pakistani negotiations on the services trade agreement . "
in a joint statement signed Sunday , the two sides reaffirmed their commitment to the construction of the sino - Pakistani economic corridor and agreed that the sino - Pakistani economic corridor is a win - win cooperative plan that will promote regional connectivity and bring prosperity and development to the entire region .
both sides agreed that the port of Gwadar was an important node for cross @-@ regional connectivity and a pillar of the China @-@ Pakistan economic corridor .
the two sides agreed to speed up the construction of the port of Gwadar and the supporting projects .
in a joint statement , china and Pakistan also expressed their opposition to negative propaganda against the china - Pakistan economic corridor .
the two sides agreed to establish a strategic dialogue between the chinese and Pakistani foreign ministers and adjust the former strategic dialogue at the level of vice foreign minister into diplomatic consultations .
in addition , the two countries will further strengthen defense cooperation and maintain high - level military exchange of visits and exchanges between various departments and levels between the two countries .
in order to further encourage foreign investors to invest in china , the chinese ministry of finance and four other ministries and commissions jointly issued a circular , saying that as of 1 january 2018 , the scope of application of the policy of temporarily not levying advance income tax on foreign investors ' profits distributed from enterprises resident in china will be extended from foreign - funded projects to all projects and fields not prohibited from foreign investment .
the ministry of finance announced in a relevant notice on its website that foreign investors are required to meet several conditions at the same time if they do not temporarily levy advance income taxes , including direct investment by foreign investors with their share of profits , including equity investment by foreign investors with their share of profits , such as capital increase , new construction , and equity takeover , but not including the addition , transfer , and acquisition of shares in listed companies ( except for qualified strategic investments ) .
it also includes dividends , dividends , and other equity investment returns resulting from the actual distribution of retained earnings to investors by resident enterprises in china .
where the profits of the foreign investor used for direct investment are paid in cash , the relevant funds are transferred directly from the account of the profit @-@ distributing enterprise to the account of the invested enterprise or the equity transferor , and the profits of the foreign investor used for direct investment are paid in kind , marketable securities and other non @-@ cash forms , the ownership of the assets is transferred directly from the profit @-@ distributing enterprise to the invested enterprise or the equity transferor is not held by other enterprises , individuals , or temporarily held , before the direct investment .
the circular also says that foreign investors who have actually recovered their direct investments that enjoy the treatment of withholding advance income tax through the method of equity transfer , repurchase , and liquidation shall , within 7 days of actually collecting the corresponding funds , report and pay back the deferred taxes to the tax authorities in accordance with the prescribed procedures .
in order to encourage foreign investors to continue to invest and operate in China , the Ministry of Finance and the Ministry of Commerce jointly issued a circular at the end of 2017 . from 1 January 2017 , the Ministry of Finance and the Ministry of Commerce will implement a deferred tax policy for those who meet the prescribed conditions and will not levy advance income tax on the profits distributed by foreign investors from resident enterprises in China .
last week , the executive meeting of the state council decided to further strengthen intellectual property protection by extending the application scope of withholding advance income tax from foreign - funded projects in the form of incentives to all non - prohibited projects and fields .
this reporter learned from the national health council that compared with a few decades ago , the incidence of undernourishment among children and teenagers in china has decreased , but the incidence of overweight obesity has markedly increased .
experts pointed out that in order to maintain a healthy body weight , the most important idea is to " cure illness " and vigorously promote scientific fitness and reasonable diet .
according to the National Health Council &apos;s recently released China Adolescent Health Education Core Information and Interpretation ( 2018 Edition ) , the key to maintaining healthy weight is eating well and exercising scientifically .
overweight , obesity and blind weight loss are all detrimental to health .
the health pitfalls behind Little Fat Pier cannot be ignored .
Ding Gang @-@ Qiang , director of the Nutrition and Health Institute of China &apos;s Centers for Disease Control and Prevention , said that overweight obesity jeopardizes the normal growth and development of teenagers , adversely affects their psychology , behavior , cognition and intelligence , and can even lead to high blood pressure , high blood sugar and high blood fat in children .
at the same time , adolescent obesity is likely to continue into adulthood , which will increase the risk of developing chronic diseases such as hypertension and diabetes in adulthood .
according to Ding Gang , the nutritional and health tests of Chinese residents in 2010 @-@ 2012 showed that 9.6 percent of Chinese children aged 6 @-@ 17 were overweight and 6.4 percent were obese , adding up to 16 percent .
at the same time , overweight obesity among children and adolescents is characterized by higher rates among boys than girls and in urban areas than in rural areas , and the rate of overweight obesity has increased markedly in recent decades .
how do teenagers cope with overweight obesity ?
Zhang Zhan , deputy director of the scientific fitness and health promotion research center of the state general administration of physical culture and sports , pointed out : at present , the main reason for teenage obesity lies in excessive calorie intake and insufficient physical activity .
for this simple obesity , attention should be paid to scientific exercise combined with reasonable dietary control .
Zhang liu pointed out : to maintain a healthy body weight , the most important concept is to " cure illness , " and a very important part of this is to conduct all - round scientific popularization education for schools , parents , and students , popularize the dangers of being overweight and obese , and raise teenagers ' awareness of the dangers of being overweight .
adolescents should be regularly examined for growth indicators such as high body weight , early detection and scientific diagnosis of overweight and obesity for timely interventions .
for adolescents who are already overweight and obese , ding gang - Qiang suggested that apart from making active and scientific arrangements for diet and exercise , teenagers should be in a special physiological stage , should avoid using hunger or semi - hunger therapy to control and reduce their weight , and should not blindly take weight - loss drugs .
( Reuters ) - On Friday , Facebook said hackers stole digital login code , giving them nearly 50 million user accounts , the most serious security vulnerability in its history .
Facebook , with more than 2.2 billion users per month , said it had not determined whether the attackers had misused any accounts or stolen personal information .
the company also failed to locate the location of the hacker and was not sure whether the hacker was targeting a particular victim .
its preliminary analysis showed that this was a wide @-@ ranging attack .
in a media conference call , CEO Zuckerberg called the incident &quot; really serious . &quot;
a spokesman for the company said his account and that of Chief Operating Officer Sheryl Sandberg were also affected .
Facebook shares fell 2.6 per cent Friday , hampering Wall Street &apos;s main index .
U. S. lawmakers said Friday the attack could increase outsiders &apos; calls for data privacy legislation .
&quot; it &apos;s another sad piece of evidence that Congress needs to take action to protect the privacy and security of social media users , &quot; Democratic Senator Mark Warner said in a statement .
&apos;i would like to have an answer to Reuters &apos; report on the security leak , &apos; said Rohit Chopra , a member of the Federal Trade Commission , on Twitter .
chinanews net Changsha , september 30 ( zheng liangtian ) september 30 is china 's fifth anniversary of martyrs .
on such a special day , family members of Hunan veterans of the war of resistance against Japanese aggression , representatives of the democratic revolution , and representatives of Hunan veterans ' homes from all walks of life came to the " tang people 's wanshou garden of the war of resistance against Japanese aggression " in Changsha city to attend a mass funeral ceremony for the 2018 martyrs ' anniversary of the war of resistance against chinese veterans , and to bid farewell to 10 veterans of the war of resistance and four veterans of the war of resistance .
" veterans of the war of resistance are witnesses to china 's war of resistance , and are true , vivid , and clear - cut teaching materials of patriotism . "
Liu xiao , former vice chairman of the Hunan provincial committee of the chinese people 's political consultative conference [ CPPCC ] , said : the patriotic spirit of heroic and courageous veterans of the war of resistance against Japanese aggression , who sacrificed their lives to forget themselves , is a precious spiritual wealth for the contemporary chinese people .
in his speech , zhu Jianjun , vice chairman of the Changsha municipal committee of the chinese people 's political consultative conference and chairman of the Changsha city CPC committee of the democratic revolution , pointed out : in recent years , the " caring for and caring for veterans of the war of resistance against Japanese aggression " project has become an excellent brand in the social service work of the Changsha city 's democratic revolution by providing services to veterans of resistance against Japanese aggression in the form of living allowances , free pensions , and free burials .
he believes that only by engraving history in our hearts can we carry forward the spirit of the war of resistance .
at eleven o &apos;clock in the morning , amid the solemn and heavy music , the people who had come to the activity stood in silence .
dressed in gowns , carrying flowers , and marching neatly , the members of the chinese etiquette team bid farewell to 10 war veterans and 4 war veterans in a tidy queue .
those who took part in the event sacrificed flowers to the war veterans , and there were many children in the crowd who joined their parents in paying homage to the war heroes .
the &quot; Manshou Garden of the Tang People &quot; is the first mausoleum in the country with the theme of the war of resistance , founded by the Changsha City Party Committee of the National Revolution and Hunan Manshou Garden Co . Ltd . , and completed in 2014 .
the first stage of the mausoleum project covers an area of over 2,000 square meters and consists of " heroic monuments , " " victorious plaza , " and " heroic mausoleum of the war of resistance .
the " mausoleum of heroes in the war of resistance against Japanese aggression " provides the tombs behind the heroes in the war of resistance against Japanese aggression free of charge , and is praised as " the last barracks for veterans in the war of resistance .
every year around the Qing Ming and National Day , large @-@ scale public sacrifices and burial ceremonies are held .
since 2015 , there have been seven mass burials of war veterans , in which 102 war veterans and partners have slept .
chinanews , yichang , october 1 ( Guo xiaoying and liu min ) the newly revised " three gorges - gezhouba water conservancy hub traffic regulation " ( hereinafter referred to as the " three gorges - gezhouba water conservancy regulation " ) will be formally implemented from october 1 , and the three gorges lifts will be formally unified with the lock after two years of trial navigation .
on the first day of implementation of the new regulations , navigation in the waters of the three gorges - gezhouba was in good order .
at 2100 hours on 30 september , the Yangtze river three gorges navigation administration announced its first security inspection plan and inspected 160 ships , a total of 124 of which passed the security inspection .
at 1400 hours on 1 october , the navigation department arranged for the first pass plan after the implementation of the new regulations .
after the implementation of the new regulations , the security inspection plan will be issued at 9 : 00 pm and 21 : 00 pm , and the crossing plan at 14 : 00 pm and 20 : 00 pm , respectively , so that ships can flexibly arrange the crossing plan .
the " dispatching regulations " have added the " classification control " principle of ship crossing the dam , defined the priority order of cross - dam vessels according to the functions and positioning of ship locks and ship lifts , and readjusted the short - line passenger vessels passing through the gates to the same priority level as demonstration ships and integrity ships .
this is also the second anniversary of the trial operation of the hoist after the formal and lock unified scheduling .
Chuan Jiang and the Three Gorges Reservoir area large and wide demonstration ship , new energy power ship also ranks first priority .
at the same time , the " regulations on dispatching " readjusted the " navigational control and management waters " from the previous 180 km of near dam waters to 541.8 km of waters from the yunyang chang Jiang bridge to the shitou chang Jiang bridge , and divided them into " core waters , near dam waters , control waters , and dispatching waters . "
this will help the ship side to select suitable waters to be locked and reduce the backlog of ships waiting to be locked in the dam area .
according to the characteristics of vessels crossing dams and waiting for gates , the " regulations on dispatching " also put forward measures to check the integrity of vessels that violate regulations , such as cancellation of declarations , and 24 - hour delay in crossing dams .
after the three gorges water storage , the navigation conditions in the reservoir area have been improved , and the rapid development of the Yangtze River shipping has been promoted .
the data show that the annual cargo throughput of the three gorges lock and gezhouba lock increased from 34.3 million tons in 2004 to 138 million tons and 140 million tons , respectively , in 2017 .
in the past two years , the three gorges lift has gone through 5,767 sea landings , with 162,200 passengers and 1,712,800 tons of cargo transported .
Chen dongyuan , deputy director of the three gorges navigation administration , said : the " regulations on dispatching " will play a positive role in promoting honest management of the gates , maintaining traffic order at the two dams ' hubs , easing pressure on ships waiting for the lock in the dam area , and enhancing their navigability .
