according to liu Changbao , responsible person of the beijing construction industry 's five - building group project , the construction area of the performing arts square project is 4,500 square meters , with a total amount of 1,182 tons of steel installed . the steel structure roof is supported by 26 suspension steel trusses , which are shaped as " butterfly wings " under the tension of the cable winch .
&quot; looking down from the sky over the performing arts square , the gorgeous roofs are like floral , dancing butterflies , and the bright colors will not fade over time , frost , rain and snow . &quot;
before that , monochrome ETFE membrane structure has been widely used in Bird &apos;s Nest , Water Cube , etc . , but the multi @-@ color jigsaw ETFE membrane structure is the first in China .
the reporter learned that because there are very few suppliers in the world who have the capability to produce various color membrane structures , every inch of membrane structure material is " precious . "
Liu Changbao said : in order to avoid problems such as overlap and " fighting " at the end of the cable , we will also innovate in using the " double ear " cable head structure to ensure that the " fighting " cable head bundle is in the correct position through specially designed fixed plugins .
