compared with other major economies , China &apos;s economic growth remains among the highest in the world .
" the fundamentals of china 's healthy and stable economic development have not changed , the conditions of the factors of production that support high - quality development have not changed , and the overall momentum of long - term stability and good development has not changed . "
&apos;we can all be optimistic about the prospects for China &apos;s economic development , &apos; Mr. Xi said .
