the " 2018 philippines ' first HSK overseas study and employment exhibition " opened on the 29 th at the guangqi school in manila , capital of the philippines . thirteen famous chinese universities , including Tsinghua university , joined hands for the first time to recruit staff from seven chinese - funded enterprises in the philippines , including china electric construction , and china international airlines .
Tsai artistic , vice chairman of the Philippine chinese education center , said that since its establishment in 1994 , the Philippine chinese education center has held 29 chinese proficiency examinations and four chinese proficiency examinations , with a total of 47,000 people taking part in the examinations .
in order to make the vast number of chinese learners in the philippines successful and useful in their studies , the first HSK overseas study and employment exhibition was held this year under the guidance of the headquarters of the Confucius institute / state han - run chinese examination international .
the Philippines pioneered the HSK Overseas Employment Exhibition Chinese universities join hands to enroll on the spot .
with more than 25,000 people taking part in the HSK test in 2017 , the Philippines has become one of the countries with the largest number of HSK test takers , said Liu Xiaolong , manager of the International Examinations Department at Confucius College / National Han Office .
he expressed the hope that chinese - speaking Filipino learners would have the opportunity to have face - to - face exchanges with the teachers of china 's first - rate universities and expand the sources of overseas students of china 's famous colleges and universities .
in his speech , Tolentino AQUINO , deputy director of the education department of the Philippine capital , said that with the introduction of more chinese language courses in public schools in the manila region , chinese language has become a very useful skill as the philippines - china relations enter the best period in history , and that china 's well - known institutions of higher learning will certainly promote educational cooperation between the two countries .
a total of 1,304 candidates from 10 schools in Metro Manila and 25 from the community sat for the HSK Level 2 to Level 6 test .
Qinghua university 's admissions office , teacher liu yuting , told zxs reporters that many Filipino students are prepared to show interest in Qinghua 's economic management , computer , and medical specialties .
he said that HSK scores above grade 5 Filipino students , can log on to the school &apos;s official website for the net .
chinanews . Com reporters saw at the exhibition stand of southwest financial and economic university that 14 students had left their intention to apply for the examination before 10 : 00 .
Ms. Bai Qiaoyan , who is in charge of enrollment , said that the university offers six kinds of scholarships to overseas students , the highest of which are chinese state government scholarships ( Ph.D. ) , exemption from paying tuition fees , provision of accommodation , and a monthly living allowance of 3,500 yuan .
Qin shanghai , dean of the institute of international education of china 's ocean university , told reporters that marine science , marine life , marine geology , aquaculture , and utilization of marine living resources are the special subjects of the university .
China has a long coastline , the Philippines is a land of thousands of islands , marine scientific research needs , can complement each other .
Tongji University Foreign Student Office Director Yu Yu said Tongji University has several of the world &apos;s top majors , including civil engineering , marine , management and so on and the Philippines needs docking .
four Filipino students are currently studying at the school .
