Washington , Nov. 5 ( Reuters ) - The United States renewed sanctions on Iran &apos;s oil and financial sector on Monday , putting more pressure on Iran to limit its missile and nuclear programs and contain its growing military and political influence in the Middle East .
the move would restore the sanctions lifted by the United States under the 2015 Iran nuclear agreement and add 300 new targets to Iran &apos;s oil , shipping , insurance and banking sectors .
details of the sanctions will be announced by Secretary of State Mike Pompeo and Finance Minister Steven Mnuchin at a press conference on 1330 GMT .
the United States says it will temporarily allow eight importers to continue buying Iranian oil , including major buyers of Iranian oil such as China , India , South Korea , Japan and Turkey , to ensure crude oil prices remain stable .
U. S. officials say those countries will put money paid to Iran into a custody account .
a few days ago , the general office of the ministry of education issued a " circular on the progress of rectification and reform of special management actions for out - of - school training institutions throughout the country . " as of 15 october 2018 , there were 400,532 out - of - school training institutions and 272,175 problem - ridden institutions nationwide , and 83,510 have been rectified and reformed , with a completion rate of 30.68 percent .
of the 6,611 institutions in Heilongjiang province that discovered problems , 2,178 have been rectified and rectified , with a completion rate of 32.95 percent .
according to the spirit of the " opinions on standardizing the development of out - of - school training institutions " issued by the general office of the state council , in order to do a good job in the work of special - purpose management and reform of out - of - school training institutions , and to ensure that the tasks of rectification and reform are completed by the end of the year , all provincial education administrative departments should study and perfect Taiwan 's accounts according to the standards and speed up the rectification and reform of accounts , and the county - level education administrative departments should , on the basis of pre - school training institutions should set up the rectification and rescheduling schedule .
those who meet the setting standards or pass the rectification and acceptance criteria shall be included in the white list and announced to the public in a timely manner .
in order to prevent parents and students from being misled and to eliminate ahead - of - standard training and false propaganda , in accordance with the principles of brevity , intuition , accuracy , and standardization , according to the students ' grades , participating disciplines , and naming the names of the classes of courses , all training institutions should submit the names , contents of the training courses , targets for enrollment , progress arrangements , and time of classes to the county - level education departments for examination and approval , and the county - level education departments should promptly complete the filing and publish them to the society .
classes that have not passed the examination and approval of the record may not be accepted for training .
teachers who have strictly mastered the qualifications of teachers and who are engaged in training in Chinese , Mathematics , English , Physics , Chemistry , Biology and other subjects shall have the corresponding qualifications .
the Fujian provincial flood prevention office announced on the 30th that in view of the fact that typhoon no. 24 " Tammy " has basically ended its impact on Fujian 's coastal and maritime areas , according to the " Fujian provincial flood prevention and control station wind emergency plan , " the emergency response to typhoon prevention will be terminated at 10 : 00 a.m . on the 30th , and all relevant localities will be able to resume normal production and living order in a timely manner .
Typhoon " Tammei " started to turn around at noon on the 29 th . it moved in a northeastern direction , gradually moving away from Fujian province . at 0800 on the 30 th , the center of the typhoon was located about 140 kilometers east - south of Kagoshima , japan .
as a result , the Fujian meteorological station lifted the " maritime gale warning no. 3 " at 0800 hours on the 30th .
before that , in order to prevent typhoon " tam Mei , " Fujian had evacuated 268 fishing boats and transferred 2,282 women and children from fishing platoons as of 11 : 00 a.m . on 28 august .
China , Vietnam hold flag raising ceremony to mark national day
&quot; it would be more shocking to see such a magnificent flag @-@ raising ceremony in the frontier than to watch the flag @-@ raising ceremony on the mainland . &quot;
on the morning of 1 january , Mr. Zhang , who had come to the estuary port of Yunnan on the sino - Vietnamese border from Sichuan , together with more than 500 officers and men , resident people , and chinese and foreign tourists , watched the national flag raising ceremony to celebrate the 69 th anniversary of the founding of the people 's republic of china .
Hekou Port is the largest port in Yunnan section of the border between China and Vietnam . it is located in Hekou County , Honghe County , Yunnan Province .
with the continuous deepening of the construction of the National &quot; Belt and Road , &quot; as one of the most convenient links between China and Southeast Asia , the entry and exit flow of estuary ports has grown steadily .
at 7 : 30 a.m . on the same day , just out of the corner of the sun , the estuary 's restricted area gathered early local people and chinese and foreign tourists at estuary to watch the flag raising ceremony .
at 0745 hours , when the flag @-@ raising ceremony started on time , the members of the guard of honor at the State Gate at the Estuary border checkpoint were vivacious and took a vigorous step to escort the flag to the flag @-@ raising platform .
after the commander gave the order to raise the national flag , the flag - raiser vigorously waved his arms and drew an arc . the bright five - star red flag spread like an " eagle spreading its wings , " and the magnificent melody of the national anthem rose slowly .
" holding national day flag raising ceremonies at every time node of great significance , such as new year 's day , spring festival , and national day , not only shows china 's image , but also inspires the patriotic feelings of the people of various nationalities in the border areas . "
the officers and men of the honor guard who attended the flag - raising ceremony said so .
it has been learned that the Guomen honor guard responsible for the flag raising ceremony at the estuary port is composed of more than 40 officers and men from various posts at the estuary border checkpoint . from the three - person flag raising group to the large - scale honor guard , this contingent has gone through more than 60 years of history and has carried out more than 70 state - level foreign affairs courtesy missions since its establishment .
the newly revised personal income tax law revised the criteria for the determination of individual income tax residents in China from one year to 183 days .
in order to maintain policy stability , china 's ministry of finance and the state administration of taxation said on the 30 th that when implementing the new personal income tax law , they will consider continuing to make preferential arrangements for people from abroad , including those from hong kong , Macao , and Taiwan .
the person in charge said : the current regulations on the implementation of the personal income tax law have special preferential provisions for tax payment by persons outside china . individuals who have no domicile in china but who have resided for more than one year and less than five years may pay personal income tax only for part of the income they receive from units or individuals inside china .
those paid abroad are not required to pay personal income tax within China .
the Ministry of Finance , the State Administration of Taxation , the State Development and Reform Commission and the Ministry of Commerce also issued a circular to expand the scope of application of the policy of withholding advance income tax from foreign investors for direct investment in the distribution of profits .
the scope of application of the policy of withholding pre @-@ mentioned income tax on foreign investors &apos; distribution of profits from resident enterprises in China for domestic direct investment for the time being shall be extended from foreign @-@ funded incentive projects to all projects and fields not prohibited from foreign investment .
during the 73rd session of the United Nations General Assembly , some positive messages were released on the Korean Peninsula issue .
South Korean President Wen Jiabao relayed North Korea &apos;s &quot; irreversible &quot; nuclear renunciation and said US President Donald Trump and North Korea &apos;s top leader Kim Jong @-@ un could meet before the end of the year .
the State Department then said Secretary of State Pompeo would visit North Korea in October to advance the implementation of the commitments made by the US and North Korean leaders at their meeting in Singapore .
since the beginning of this year , the DPRK and rok have broken the ice and opened the road of dialogue . leaders of the DPRK and rok and the DPRK and the united states have held meetings . the general trend of easing the situation on the peninsula has continued , and the principle of dialogue to resolve the Korean peninsula issue has also been upheld .
first , the point that " the essence of the Korean peninsula issue is a security issue " has not changed . to realize peace on the peninsula , the key lies in properly and well resolving the legitimate security concerns of all sides , rather than simply putting pressure on the other side and persistently emphasizing its own claims .
second , during the dialogue on realizing the denuclearization of the peninsula , the parties concerned still held different views on the steps and modalities for realizing the denuclearization of the peninsula . due to the long - standing lack of political trust between the DPRK and the united states , the game thinking of " who is first and who is next " remained strong .
at the recent open meeting of the un security council on the Korean peninsula , held at the un headquarters in new york , different voices on the issue of sanctions against the DPRK once again highlighted that these two points " have not changed . "
us secretary of state Pompeau insists that sanctions against the DPRK will not be lifted until the Korean peninsula is completely denuclearized .
Russian foreign minister Sergei Lavrov , on the other hand , stressed the principle of " action in response to action , " saying : " the trend of weakening sanctions should be the same as the steps taken by the DPRK in gradually abandoning its nuclear program . "
there is no doubt that the parties concerned should continue to fully , completely and accurately implement the Security Council resolutions relating to the Democratic People &apos;s Republic of Korea , but pressure is not an end in itself , and the implementation of sanctions and the promotion of a political settlement are demands of the Council resolutions , and there is no alternative .
just as Wang Yi , chinese state councilor and foreign minister , said , in view of the current positive developments in DPRK - rok and DPRK - us relations , the chinese side believes it is necessary for the security council to consider initiating reversible clauses in due course so as to encourage the DPRK and all parties concerned to take greater steps toward denuclearization .
in retrospect , the denuclearization of the peninsula and every progress in the peace process require sufficient political courage on all sides .
at present , in the face of the increasingly high expectations of the international community for the promotion of a political solution to the Korean peninsula issue , all parties concerned should , in particular , display political courage , make political decisions , implement commitments , resolve difficult problems , continue to take steps toward one another , advance the process of denuclearization of the peninsula in parallel with the establishment of a peace mechanism on the peninsula , and jointly create permanent peace on the peninsula .
the Hukou waterfall scenic spot in linfen city , Shanxi province , will maintain a relatively high water level during the national day and will not meet the conditions for opening .
to ensure safety , the scenic spots are temporarily closed during the National Day .
Hukou Falls of Yellow River is the second largest waterfall in China , the largest yellow waterfall in the world .
the Yellow River runs to this point , the two sides of the strait rocky cliff , the mouth of the river as narrow as the mouth of a kettle , forming the &quot; Yellow River a kettle &quot; spirit .
according to this reporter , every june - october is the flood season of the yellow river . starting from july 12 , 2018 , due to the high water level of the yellow river , the Hukou scenic area of the yellow river in Shanxi began to be closed one after another . therefore , the Hukou scenic area has been closed for nearly a month .
Ni yufeng , chief engineer of the hukou scenic spot management committee , told the media that this is the longest time in the past 20 years that the water level in the Yellow river has lasted for the longest time . " we have not had such a long time before . in 2017 , our flood season will be closed for four days , and this year will be nearly a month . "
it has been learned that originally , in order to prepare for the golden week of 11 november , the hukou waterfall scenic area of the huanghe river in Shanxi had increased personnel arrangements and vehicle maintenance ahead of schedule , and even temporary personnel had been hired .
according to the " circular on doing a good job in flood prevention in the yellow river during the national day period " issued by the " office of the general headquarters for flood prevention and drought control of the yellow river , " inner mongolia , Shanxi , Shaanxi , Henan , and Shandong provinces are required to do a good job in flood prevention work in the yellow river during the national day .
at present , the main flow of the Yellow River is relatively large , with upstream flow maintained at 2,000 @-@ 3,000 cubic metres per second , middle @-@ stream flow maintained at 2,500 @-@ 3,500 cubic metres per second and downstream flow maintained at 3,000 cubic metres per second .
provision of Influenza Vaccination Services at Health Centres and Health Centres during National Day Holidays
the Health Bureau has ordered 150,000 doses of the four @-@ priced influenza vaccine for 2018 @-@ 2019 this year . at this stage , priority is given to high @-@ risk groups . to facilitate residents to vaccinate against influenza during the holidays , the Health Centres and Health Centres of the Health Bureau provide vaccination services from 9 : 00 a.m. to 1 : 00 noon on National Day ( 1 and 2 October ) .
in addition to the above @-@ mentioned convenience measures , the health centres and health posts of the Health Bureau have extended their influenza vaccination service from Monday to Friday to 8 p.m. As at 4 : 00 p.m. on September 30 , 4,158 people have been vaccinated , up from 3,714 in the same period last year .
free vaccinations are provided to the following Macao residents : persons aged 6 months to under 18 , persons aged 50 and over , pregnant women , all patients with chronic diseases , including obese persons ( i.e. persons with BMI of 30 or more ) , as well as staff of institutions , nurseries , kindergartens , primary schools , secondary schools , all health workers , and Macao residents working in gambling and entertainment establishments .
at the same time , other persons deemed necessary by the Health Bureau , including the public sector , will actively contact the relevant institutions to obtain the list and arrange for the vaccination at the Health Centre .
to facilitate vaccinators and reduce the waiting time for vaccination , the Health Bureau will send health care workers to our secondary schools , primary schools , kindergartens and nurseries from October to December this year to provide group vaccination against influenza to children , small and medium @-@ sized children , teachers and staff . in addition , it will arrange group vaccinations in residential care homes for the elderly , the public sector or other institutions with a large number of people .
students and young children who are unable to take part in group vaccinations may , as of December 3 , 2018 , obtain a Macao Resident Identity Card , Health Bureau User Card , Influenza Vaccination Card ( if any ) , Student Identity Card , Employee Identity Card or Occupational Document at the Count of Renmin General Hospital inoculation Station or Health Centre .
the Health Bureau reminds residents that between September 2017 and August 2018 , persons who have been vaccinated against influenza 2017 @-@ 2018 will still need to be vaccinated against the new season of influenza from September 2018 , as the Northern Hemisphere flu vaccine for 2018 @-@ 2019 contains an updated version of the influenza antigen targeting the Northern Hemisphere for the winter of 2018 @-@ 2019 and the summer of 2019 .
the peak period of influenza in Macau usually occurs between January and March each year . it is later than in temperate areas ( such as northern China and Japan ) . the Health Bureau urges the elderly , children , pregnant women , obese people and people with chronic diseases , who are at higher risk of complications after infection , to be vaccinated as soon as possible .
