in response to the incident in which a pupil in Suining was physically punished by a teacher for doing the wrong thing , the official microblog of the Heidong new district management committee of Suining city issued a circular yesterday , saying that it had been verified that Luo XX , a teacher of Suzhou primary foreign language school , had physically punished a pupil . he had been transferred from his post and that the school involved was disqualified from the annual " evaluation of excellence . "
a few days ago , parents reported that girls in the sixth grade of a primary school in Suining were beaten by class maths teachers at school for doing wrong problems , causing widespread concern .
afterwards , the social undertakings bureau of the new district of Heidong in Suining city set up an investigation team to investigate , inquire into , collect evidence on the spot , and transfer the teachers involved from their posts .
yesterday , Suining Heidong New District Management Committee issued an official Weibo information circular , Suzhou foreign language primary school teacher Luo XX verified the situation of corporal punishment of students .
through research , the end @-@ of @-@ year examination of Suzhou Foreign Languages Primary School &quot; one vote rejected &quot; , annulled the annual &quot; merit evaluation &quot; qualification .
the circular also said : we should conduct collective commandment talks with the administrative team of the Suzhou foreign language primary school , handle the leaders and class leaders according to the relevant regulations , severely punish the teachers involved , and order the Suzhou foreign language primary school to carry out an in - depth inspection and carry out construction activities for teachers and moral teachers , and take practical measures to prevent the recurrence of such incidents .
