Shenzhen , october 1 ( zheng xiaohong , Xu dianwei , liu yingmeng ) on october 1 , the first day of the " golden week " of the mainland 's national day , and also the last day of the hong kong national day public holiday , many mainland residents took advantage of their holidays to go abroad to play and shop . there were also many hong kong residents who returned to hong kong on that day . Shenzhen ports experienced a " bursting " of passenger flow . the Luohu and Shenzhen bay ports opened 22 new self - service channels to improve the efficiency of customs clearance .
according to the data provided by the Shenzhen border inspection station , by 16:00 on the same day , the number of people entering and leaving the Shenzhen port had reached more than 429,000 , and the number of transportation facilities had reached more than 16,800 . all ports were busy all the time and maintained a good order of entry and exit .
it has been learned that under the influence of many favorable factors , such as the increase in the number of countries providing visa - free access for chinese citizens , the number of tourists going to europe , southeast asia , and other countries for holiday shopping has continued to increase during the national day holidays .
on the morning of 1 january , the passenger flow at lo wu , Shenzhen bay , Huanggang , and Fukuda control points reached a peak , with the passenger flow at lo wu control point continuing from 9 : 00 am to 11 : 00 am and the passenger flow at Shenzhen bay control point from 6.30 am to 13 : 00 noon .
it has been learned that in order to cope with the peak flow of passengers ( cars ) entering and leaving the country , the Shenzhen frontier control station , in accordance with the unified arrangements made by the state immigration administration , has started the service pattern during peak periods of passenger ( cars ) traffic . it has arranged for overtime police forces to support the frontline of duty , opened sufficient inspection channels ahead of schedule , guided passengers and vehicles to wait in an orderly manner for inspection , ensured that chinese citizens ' entry and exit customs clearance queues do not exceed 30 minutes , while taking into account the efficiency of foreigners , strengthened the maintenance of order in areas with heavy traffic , and ensured that customs clearance is safe and orderly .
at the same time , the Shenzhen border control station reminds passengers entering and leaving the country to pay attention to the validity of their travel documents , visas and endorsements , rationally arrange their itinerary , avoid rush hours as far as possible , and choose the right time and the right port to travel .
passengers travelling on the Guangzhou @-@ Shenzhen high @-@ speed rail to Hong Kong must hold valid exit / entry documents and visa endorsements . high @-@ speed rail tickets are only valid for travel . they cannot be used as exit / entry documents . if they are unable to leave Hong Kong for any reason , they should follow the guidelines of the police on border inspection and wait at designated places for MTR Company staff to guide them to go back to the Mainland .
systemic lupus erythematosus is a chronic disease that involves multiple organs throughout the body and was previously considered an &quot; incurable disease . &quot;
it should not be cured because of its unknown pathogenesis , difficult diagnosis and treatment , and lack of effective treatment methods .
recently , Liu Wanli , a researcher at Tsinghua University &apos;s College of Life Sciences , and Li Zhanguo , director of the Rheumatic Immunization Center at Peking University &apos;s People &apos;s Hospital , jointly discovered that human immunoglobulins exhibit molecular variations that increase systemic lupus erythematosus susceptibility , and are involved in regulating immune B cells .
in short , the two teams confirmed that an abnormal immune molecule in humans is an important cause of systemic lupus erythematosus .
according to sun xiaolin of beijing people 's hospital , one of the authors of the article , the chestnut - Zhanguo team collected nearly 2,000 large samples of systemic lupus erythematosus patients and conducted research , and discovered that the incidence and severity of inflammation in the body , such as autoantibodies , nephritis , arthritis , plasma , and vasculitis , had increased markedly in a wide variety and large number of patients with immunoglobulin the body .
Liu Wanli &apos;s team discovered the pathway of immune signal activated by molecular mutation through various research methods , such as immune cell tracing , animal experiments and sequencing , and promoted the pathogenesis of B cells secreting a variety of autoantibodies .
the reporter learned that the two teams are strongly united , give full play to their respective advantages , and realize the close combination of basic research and clinical application .
Liu Wanli &apos;s team was dedicated to the study of B lymphocyte immune recognition and activation , while the Chestnut Zhanguo team was involved in the long @-@ term clinical study of systemic lupus erythematosus .
&quot; the study is one of the achievements of many years of collaboration between the two teams and is the first time that the academic community has recognized that immunoglobulin gene abnormalities will induce systemic lupus erythematosus , laying a solid foundation for further academic research and clinical targeting .
this is not to protect the weak , but to act in accordance with the law .
the lawyer brought an axe to court ?
the news was really exciting at first glance , and it blew up in the legal circle .
Zhongfa of Quanzhou City , Fujian Province , subsequently fined 500 yuan to lawyers involved in the case , and proposed in writing that the Quanzhou City Bar Association carry out investigation and handling .
according to a report by the xinjing bao , the Quanzhou city law association recently issued an official circular saying that the acts of the two lawyers do not involve violations of the law and regulations , and they will not be punished according to law .
according to many reports , Quanzhou City Law Association &apos;s handling is not to protect the short or engage in confrontation , but has been approved by the Quanzhou Intermediate Court .
an incident that could have sparked tensions within the legal community was eventually resolved properly .
the reversal of events stemmed from a more complete reversion of the truth : the axe carried by the lawyer in question was of the same style and model as the defendant &apos;s murder weapon , but it was not opened , was used only as corroborative evidence at the evidentiary examination stage , and did not have the subjective intention of intimidating or &quot; endangering the security of the court . &quot;
there are four very important details for judging whether the lawyer in question acted in violation of the law and regulations : first , the local court held two previous sessions and produced only photographs of the axe , which were necessary from the point of view of the defence ; second , the axe was purchased only one hour before the trial , and the lawyer was not unwilling to seek the judge &apos;s consent , but objectively failed to contact the judge ; third , the entire axe was not overheated or improperly used ; and fourth , the matter was publicly acknowledged to the lawyer .
combining these circumstances , it can be seen that the lawyer involved " brought an axe to court " was not guilty of any evil , but merely for the purpose of defending his case .
after clarifying the whole fact , Quanzhou City Law Association did not push the boat , but resisted pressure to make a decision not to punish .
this decision also stands the test of fact and law .
as for bringing the axe used as a control tool to court without the permission of the court , it is indeed fraught with unease and misunderstanding .
for reasons of safety and caution , the Quanzhou Intermediate Court had previously imposed fines and judicial advice .
in order to preserve the dignity of lawyers and prevent individual courts from using excuses to harass lawyers , the Supreme Law issued the Rules on Security Examination by the Judicial Police of the People &apos;s Court in 2014 , establishing the principle that lawyers need not undergo a physical security examination in order to appear in court .
since the issuance of the rule , a wide range of lawyers have set an example and few incidents have occurred that jeopardize the security of the Tribunal because of security vulnerabilities .
in rare cases like Quanzhou , misunderstandings can easily be dispelled as long as they are communicated in a spirit of mutual respect and understanding .
the Bar Association , as a self @-@ governing organization of the legal profession , has the dual mission of punishing wrongdoing and safeguarding legality .
in the past , individual law associations were criticized for their emphasis on discipline and their failure to protect their interests .
and Quanzhou Law Association &apos;s decision , both in terms of process and result , is laudable , setting an example for more law associations to perform their duties correctly .
what tax benefits will affect our purse from October 1 st ?
Xinhua news agency , Shanghai , october 1 ( reporter san tong ) the new personal income tax law will come into effect on january 1 , 2019 . in order to enable the broad masses of the people to enjoy the tax reduction dividends as soon as possible , from october 1 , they will first deduct the actual wages and salaries earned by taxpayers at the starting point of 5,000 yuan per month and apply the new tax rate scale .
with the New Deal on the ground , what benefits will affect the masses of money bags ?
advantages : 1 ) obvious tax reduction in salary and salary income
taxpayers who receive wages after October 1 can deduct a basic deduction of $ 5,000 per month and apply a new tax rate scale . most taxpayers have different degrees of tax reduction , especially for middle and low @-@ income earners .
according to the tax reduction tables for different income groups , those who earn 8,000 yuan , 10,000 yuan , 20,000 yuan , and 50,000 yuan a month after deducting the " three risks and one gold " will pay taxes of 90 yuan , 290 yuan , 1,590 yuan , and 9,090 yuan respectively after the tax reform . the corresponding tax reduction rates are 73.9 percent , 61.1 percent , 49.0 percent , and 18.8 percent , respectively , compared with the starting point of 3,500 yuan a month .
it is worth noting that due to holiday reasons , the new basic fee reduction and tax rate schedule can be applied to all units ' legally issued wages at the end of september that should have been paid in october .
to this end , the tax department uniformly popularized the use of the withholding client software has provided the corresponding tax calculation function , but the corresponding taxes still have to be declared within the statutory filing period .
pros and cons 2 : lower tariff range significantly widened
in addition to raising the threshold , a new rate scale will apply from 1 October .
this time , the seven - step tax rate for wages and salaries has remained the same as before , but there has been a marked change in the tax rate scale . the three - step low tax rate scale of 3 percent , 10 percent , and 20 percent has been significantly expanded , and the 25 percent tax rate scale has been reduced . the three - step high tax rate of 30 percent , 35 percent , and 45 percent has remained unchanged .
it is worth noting that the tax law also readjusted the tax rate on income from production and business operations , and the lower limit of the top 35 percent tax rate was raised from 100,000 yuan to 500,000 yuan .
this means that individual businesses and sole proprietorships will all benefit from the tax reform .
" judging from the previous estimates of tax cuts for individual taxpayers in Shanghai , the broad masses of taxpayers will fully feel the dividends of the tax reform , and in particular , the tax cuts for low and middle - income people will be noticeable . "
Lanmin , head of the personal income tax department of the Shanghai tax bureau of the State Administration of Taxation .
advantages and disadvantages : more convenient and optimized tax services
since the promulgation of the new Personal Income Tax Law , Shanghai &apos;s tax authorities have launched a series of comprehensive and extensive tax publicity activities .
on the one hand , key tax sources , key enterprises to develop &quot; one @-@ on @-@ one , point @-@ to @-@ point &quot; policy guidance .
the tax bureau of the Pudong new district successively visited large enterprises such as Apple trade ( Shanghai ) company limited , zifu bao ( china ) network technology company limited , and hong xing meikailong household group limited . these enterprises have a large number of employees , a large amount of withholding and payment work , and tax departments have taken the initiative to provide guidance and answer questions and answers . Xu hui district tax bureau visited the zhongzhi financial consulting company limited , the zhongzhi economic and technological cooperation company of the large labor enterprises in the region to collect concerns and resolve their claims in a timely manner .
on the other hand , to the broad masses of taxpayers , launch the &quot; all @-@ round , multi @-@ dimensional , three @-@ dimensional &quot; tax policy .
Shanghai tax official website , Weixin public number , Weibo channels in time to promote policy hot spots to ensure that the policy publicity is in place .
meanwhile , on 28 september , the Shanghai tax micro - trust public number 12366 intelligent consulting platform launched a " target - oriented " integrated tax reform propaganda service through the " manual + intelligent " tax service consultation .
