crab farmers , who have been dealing with hairy crabs for nearly 20 years , are planning to export crab seedlings and breeding techniques from yangcheng lake hairy crabs to Thailand so that aquatic cuisine can cross national borders and promote cultural exchanges with overseas cuisine .
