Xinhua International Time Review : defending multilateralism , China knows what to do .
at a time when the counter @-@ currents of unilateralism are surging , international rules and the multilateral order are under attack .
to some extent , the confrontation between unilateralism and multilateralism has entered a critical period .
as a responsible big country , China has joined the international community in upholding multilateralism and pushing forward multilateralism with the idea of following the general trend and conforming to the main road , and with solid and effective actions .
in the face of the new situation and new challenges , China is making a resounding voice on the direction and path of development of multilateralism .
as Wang Yi , state councilor and minister for foreign affairs , said in his speech at the general debate of the 73rd session of the united nations general assembly , multilateralism in the new era should adhere to the goal of cooperation and win - win progress , be based on the rule of law , be based on the essence of fairness and justice , and be guided by effective action .
at the same time , China called for a global pattern of development cooperation , with the United Nations at its core and North @-@ South cooperation as the main channel , complemented by South @-@ South cooperation , and for all parties to work together to build a community of destiny for humanity .
China 's thinking and voice reflect the mainstream voice of the international community .
as Espinosa , President of the seventy @-@ third session of the General Assembly , said , &quot; More than ever before , the United Nations needs to promote multilateralism and uphold a rules @-@ based international system . &quot;
IMF Managing Director Lagarde said the international community should continue to firmly uphold the multilateral trading system , adhere to international trade rules and resolve differences through consultations .
in recent years , as a result of the adjustment in the balance of global economic and political power , a number of emerging markets and groups of developing countries have emerged to play a greater role in the major international multilateral mechanisms and to provide a new impetus for development in the face of adverse winds of multilateralism .
taking this dimension into consideration , china advocates the idea of building a big family rather than patching up small circles , adhering to the concept of multilateralism such as jointly discussing common construction rather than engaging in winner - take - all , and following the trend of the times . this is the inevitable choice for dealing with global challenges and solving world problems , and represents the common aspirations of most countries in the world .
have advanced ideas , more solid action .
China &apos;s &quot; One Belt , One Road &quot; initiative has become the largest platform for international cooperation .
the international and regional cooperation initiatives initiated by China , such as the &quot; One Belt , One Road , &quot; the Asian Infrastructure Investment Bank and the &quot; 16 + 1 Cooperation , &quot; promote international regional cooperation , perfect and supplement the existing international system and order , bring innovative vitality to multilateral cooperation and contribute to the development of the international order in a more just and rational direction .
as a defender of the international order and practitioner of multilateralism , China &apos;s actions in the multilateral arena of the United Nations are becoming increasingly powerful .
good offices to address climate change , participate in peacekeeping operations , reduce poverty and help other countries implement the 2030 sustainable development agenda .
as United Nations Secretary @-@ General Guterres has said , China has become an important pillar of multilateralism .
when the &quot; trust deficit &quot; facing the world grows , and when populism and polarization rise , it is the world &apos;s most urgent need for multilateral cooperation .
at such a historic juncture , the international community needs to join hands to translate consensus into action , resolutely defend multilateralism and work together to build a community of destiny for humanity .
