according to past experience , places where people are concentrated , bus hubs , and bus and subway lines , including the crowds watching the raising of flags in Tiananmen square , are all key areas of their work .
in the crowd , the civilian police in civilian clothes looked calmly at the passing crowd .
at about 7 : 00 a.m . , investigators crouching at the bus stop spotted two suspicious men following a male passenger on the 20 th bus from the Yongding gate .
