six @-@ year interval Tencent welcomes major organisational changes - CITIC Network
Tencent announced on the 30 th that it would officially launch a new round of overall strategic upgrading , and that the organizational structure would usher in a new round of optimization adjustments after a lapse of six years , with reorganization and consolidation based on the original seven enterprise groups ( BG ) , saying that the readjustment would not involve layoffs .
Tencent new six major business groups .
two new business groups emerged after six years of realignment .
it has been learned that the new enterprise group not only maintains the advantages and characteristics of the deep - ploughing vertical field , but also retains the original enterprise development enterprise group ( CDG ) , interactive entertainment enterprise group ( IEG ) , technical engineering enterprise group ( TEG ) , and microtelecommunications enterprise group ( WXG ) . it also focuses on the integration effect , and the newly established cloud and intelligent industry enterprise group ( CSIG ) , platform , and content enterprise group ( PCIG ) .
the reporter noted that Tencent &apos;s original mobile internet business group ( MIG ) and former network media business group ( OMG ) all disappeared , especially OMG , and that the outside world was very well known .
Tencent said the newly created platform and content group , known as the Platform &amp; Content Group , would organically disassemble and reorganize the highly relevant and integrated segments of the former social networking consortium , the former mobile Internet consortium , and the former online media consortium , including social platforms , traffic platforms , digital content , and core technology .
and the new CSIG , or Cloud and Smart Industries Group , will consolidate industry solutions such as Tencent Cloud , Internet + , Smart Retail , Education , Health , Security , and LBS to boost digitization .
Ma huateng , chairman of Tencent 's board of directors and chief executive officer , said that the second half of the internet belongs to the industrial internet . in the first half , Tencent will provide users with high - quality services through connections . in the second half , we will help the industry and consumers form a new and more open connection ecology .
in response to the &quot; layoff &quot; rumor : clear no layoffs .
Tencent released news of the organizational restructuring , there is news that the restructuring will involve layoffs .
Tencent related parties told CNS that " it is clear that this organizational restructuring will not involve layoffs . we will shift the business modules as a whole and combine them before optimizing them . "
