this newspaper ( internship reporter Li Qiyao ) in recent years , there have been many campus plastic runway failure incidents .
to this end , the Ministry of Education has issued a circular requiring the implementation of the new national standard for surface sports areas of synthetic materials for primary and secondary schools delivered for use after 1 November of this year .
the mandatory national standard , " surface sports ground for synthetic materials in primary and secondary schools , " was drafted by the ministry of education , with the participation of 26 scientific research institutes and testing institutions . after more than two years of revision , more than 100 expert meetings were organized to demonstrate the situation , as well as on - site inspections and sampling tests nationwide , and countless verification experiments were collected for the products of hundreds of enterprises on the market .
compared with the old national standard of 2005 , this reporter discovered that the new national standard has not only changed from the " national recommended standard " to the " national mandatory standard , " but has also added many contents , including requirements for thickness , physical properties , aging resistance , inorganic filler content , anti - skid granule polymer content , limit for harmful substances in finished surface products , and limit for non - solid and solid raw materials .
in particular , the new national standard limits the number of hazardous substances that may be produced in the construction of plastic runways on campus , from 7 to 18 , and regulates the amount of volatile organic substances in the runway after completion in accordance with the home installation standards .
if the Harmful Substances Limits and odour Requirements for Setting @-@ in @-@ Plate and Prefabricated Surface Products clearly provide for the release of hazardous substances , the total volatile organic compounds shall not exceed 5 mg / m3 , formaldehyde shall not exceed 0.4 mg / m3 , carbon sulfide shall not exceed 7 mg / m3 , benzene shall not exceed 0.1 mg / m3 and the odour level shall not exceed 3 .
the new national standard also makes detailed stipulations on sampling requirements , inspection rules and adjudication rules for plastic runways in primary and secondary schools .
in addition , the campus artificial turf also included the national standard mandatory testing scope for the first time .
in the near future , all localities should carry out special work arrangements for the implementation of the new national standards , and report the implementation of the new national standards to the department of physical health and arts education of the ministry of education within the year .
chengdu , september 30 ( Wang yu ) on the afternoon of the 30 th , the 2018 women 's table tennis world cup finals staged the " national table tennis civil war . "
in the end , Grand slam winner Ding Ning 4 : 0 Rick home game teammate Zhu Yueling , after four years , again won the championship of the women &apos;s table tennis world cup , which is the 21st time that Chinese women won the championship of the event .
Ding Ning and Zhu Yueling are both teammates and friends , and both sides are quite familiar with each other &apos;s skills and tactics .
both sides followed suit , both in preparation and in preparation for the game .
entering the final , the two agreed that they had completed the task .
however , the contest between ding ning and zhu yueling in the competition can be described as a swordsmanship .
in the first set , Ding Ning , who had the most experience in the competition , led by 3 : 1 , and Zhu Yueling followed up the score by using Ding Ning &apos;s mistakes .
then zhu yuling 's errors in the offensive began to increase , and ding ning seized the opportunity to lead by 3 : 9 : 5 in a row and took the lead in winning the situation by 10 : 6 .
although Zhu Yueling chased three points at a time , Ding Ning still used the serve to get the first game at 11 : 9 .
in the second set , Zhu Yu @-@ ling &apos;s mistake remained high , with Tingning taking advantage of its 6 : 1 lead .
Zhu Yueling , who lagged behind at 2 : 7 , scored 2 points by changing her rhythm and then used her attack to chase the score to 8 : 9 .
at the crucial moment , Tinning scored 2 points 11 : 8 to win another game .
in the third set , the two began to bite more tightly into 3 : 3 level .
Tingning then lost three more points in the attack , but she then used the sharp attack to score three points to score six points .
Zhu Yueling scored 2 points to re - establish the advantage , and took the lead in getting the situation by 10 : 8 .
but Tingning was so fierce that he won the third set at 12 : 10 after scoring four points .
in the fourth set , zhu yuling took the lead by 4 : 2 .
since then , however , Tingning has shown an extremely strong offensive position , scoring 4 points at a time to stop Zhu Yueling .
after a pause , Zhu Yueling recovered some of the status , gradually chasing the score to 8 : 8 level .
at the crucial moment , Tingning had no soft hands and scored 2 points in a row to get the match .
with Zhu Yueling back out of the game , Tingning 4 : 0 sweep the opponents to win the championship .
last month , Tingning came to Chengdu after winning her 14 @-@ month @-@ old championship title in the Bulgarian Open , even though she said before the match that she had not set a goal for the race and that she had finished the semifinals in the morning by saying she had completed her task .
Tingning finally beat teammate Zhu Yueling to win her third World Cup title , and she was satisfied with her performance : &quot; a championship is important to every athlete .
I did not think of this before the game , just said a game to fight , the final play itself is very satisfactory . "
Chu Yueling , who fought at home , won a silver medal and failed to achieve her goal of defending the crown . on the question of whether the enthusiastic spectators at home would exert invisible pressure on themselves , she said : " I think i can handle the whole game in terms of pressure . today tinning played very well , so i have not yet found a rhythm . "
to activate rural consumption , we should rely on the normal mechanism to purify the market , guide the demand for healthy consumption , and enhance the sense of peasants ' consumption .
the figures show that the consumption potential of rural residents has been continuously released , with retail sales of rural consumer goods growing by 10.5 percent in the first half of this year , 1.3 percentage points higher than in cities and towns .
during a visit to a impoverished village in a certain county in western china , there was only one convenience store in the village . when entering the store , some commodities seemed to have known each other before . " goldfish " was marked as " golden dragon oil " and " wangtsai " became " strong milk " and " shanzhai " commodities .
over the past few years , similar phenomena have frequently come to light . some rural fake and inferior commodities have similar names and similar packaging .
according to a consumer survey released by a city in the western region , the problem of over - counterfeiting in rural areas is serious , with 66 percent of users buying fake goods in supermarkets under the township line , of which more than half have food products .
the departments concerned are trying to improve the rural market . why is it that " li ghosts " continue to fight year after year ?
unlike the urban market , peasants ' awareness of protecting their rights and interests is relatively weak . in addition , many rural areas are remote and are in blind areas beyond the reach of the supervisory forces . this has given rise to a breeding ground for fake and inferior commodities .
a commodity with many heads , some departments with prices , some departments with production , some with markets , some with overlapping functions , and some with annual holidays . a gust of wind has been concentrated on the management of fake goods , and the fakes have gradually emerged . just after the old ones were finished , new ones have emerged .
in the absence of a long - term supervision and control mechanism , it is difficult to purify the rural market , the cost of violating the law is low , and the benefits are large . as a result , some illegal merchants and sellers have set up crooked ideas of " going up to the mountains and going down to the countryside , " and some rural areas have become " extinct markets . "
from subsistence to well - off , the broad masses of farmers are moving toward development - oriented consumption .
a few days ago , the CPC central committee and the state council issued " some opinions on perfecting the mechanism for promoting the consumption system and further arousing the consumption potential of the residents , " which proposed promoting the upgrading of the consumption ladder of the rural residents , with the aim of enabling the broad masses of peasants to " consume " " willing to " consume " and " dare to consume " so that rural consumption can really flourish .
on the one hand , it is necessary to deepen reform , eliminate the malpractice of multiple administrative departments and multiple management of the market , and improve the food safety and product quality supervision network in light of local conditions , so as to continuously reduce the space for making and selling fake products in rural areas .
on the other hand , it is necessary to intensify law enforcement , open up and supervise " capillaries , " and never allow fake and inferior products to breed and spread in rural areas .
severely punishing the peasants in the pit is the only way to protect the peasants . no matter how hidden the counterfeiters hide , they should not be the reason for the breeding of fake and inferior commodities . the relevant departments should clearly define their duties and responsibilities . the grass - roots supervision and control forces should sink . if any link goes wrong , they should be held accountable , so that the counterfeiters and sellers will have no place to hide .
we must strictly close market access , strictly examine the qualifications of production and business operators , control the circulation of the market , let the products come and go straight and clear , and find ways and means at the source and at the root to enable legitimate dealers to operate in peace of mind and reassure peasants to buy them .
activate rural consumption and guide the demand for healthy consumption .
along with the upgrading of consumption , many peasants not only seek to eat enough and eat well , but also pursue high - quality life , such as culture and health , so that they cannot compare the rural market with " low - quality " and " cheap " paintings .
this requires promoting the extension of e - commerce to the vast number of rural areas , opening up two - way sales channels between urban and rural areas , promoting the integration of off - line industrial development platforms and on - line electronic commerce trading platforms , supporting the development of new consumption business models into rural markets , promoting the organic integration of commercial and commercial logistics with leisure agriculture , rural tourism , and product processing , and so on , improving the modern rural circulation network system , optimizing the integration of stock resources , and effectively reducing the cost of rural circulation .
to create a clear and reassuring market environment for the rural areas , so that farmers do not worry about spending , rural consumption will become more and more prosperous , can enhance the sense of access to and happiness of farmers .
China will lower its MFN tariff rate on some goods from november 1 , and the total tariff level will be reduced to 7.5 percent
according to the decision of the 26th executive meeting of the state council , the state council 's tariff rules committee issued a notice on 30 november to lower the most - favored nation [ MFN ] tariff rate for some commodities from 1 november 2018 .
according to the " notice of the state council 's tariff committee on reducing import tariffs on some commodities , " in order to meet the needs of industrial upgrading , reducing enterprise costs , and satisfying the multi-level consumption of the masses , the MFN rate for some industrial products and other commodities will be lowered from 1 november this year .
there are 1,585 tax items , accounting for about 19 percent of china 's total tax items , and the average tax rate has dropped from 10.5 percent to 7.8 percent , an average decrease of 26 percent .
the reduction mainly covers textiles ; stone , ceramics , glass products ; some iron and steel and base metal products ; electrical and mechanical equipment and parts such as metalworking machinery , textile machinery , engineering machinery , transmission equipment , electrical equipment , instruments and instruments ; and resource - oriented commodities and primary processing products such as non - metallic mines , inorganic chemicals , wood and paper products , and precious jade .
at the same time , with the lowering of the overall tariff level , especially the import tariffs on pharmaceuticals and consumer goods , the tariff rates on imports of imported goods will be lowered accordingly .
in order to implement the policy decisions and arrangements of the CPC central committee and the state council , china has imposed zero tariffs on the vast majority of imported pharmaceuticals since 1 may this year , lowered import tariffs on automobiles , parts and components , and some consumer goods for daily use since 1 july , and implemented the third step of lowering taxes on information technology [ it ] agreement extension products .
the reporter learned from the state council 's customs and excise commission that since the beginning of this year , china 's total tariff level will drop from 9.8 percent in 1999 to 7.5 percent , an average reduction of 23 percent .
appropriately lowering tariffs is conducive to promoting the balanced development of foreign trade and promoting a higher level of opening up to the outside world . it is also conducive to making overall use of both international and domestic resources and promoting domestic supply - side structural reform .
a responsible person of the committee said : this year marks the 40th anniversary of reform and opening up . the initiative to lower the general level of tariffs is a practical action to implement the spirit of general secretary xi Jinping 's important speech at the Boao forum for asia . it is also an important measure for china to further open up to the outside world and take the initiative to expand imports in light of its own high - quality development needs . this action and measure shows that china will unswervingly pursue a win - win opening strategy for mutual benefit . while strengthening its own development momentum , it will also enable china to better benefit the world .
on 29 september , a regional public branding conference for agricultural products was held in the Nankai district of Tianjin city .
Red Army millet , black beans , mountain boy goat herding , hard buckwheat tea , paper @-@ cut leather album , pure hand slippers . . . . . . . well @-@ packed agricultural products neatly placed on the stand , they have a common brand name called &quot; the townsman . &quot;
" building a regional brand of ' huanxiang people ' has effectively solved the bottleneck of the development of agricultural products in huanxian county , which is " many but scattered , small , and weak , " and has also become a powerful carrier for tackling tough problems in poverty . " on 29 august , a regional public branding conference for agricultural products sponsored by huanxiang people was held in Nankai district , Tianjin city .
located at the junction of the three provinces and regions of Shaanxi Ganning , huanxian county has a long history and is rich in resources as a " advanced county in national grain production " and a " small grocery town in china " .
lamb , yellow rice wine , buckwheat chopped noodles , swallow noodles and other local snacks are often remembered by tourists in other places .
as China &apos;s urbanization level continues to rise and the urban population grows rapidly , a large number of young rural people leave their hometowns and begin to live in cities .
Yang Qiaojia , an expert in agricultural brand research in china , said : " nowadays , urban life is fast and stressful , and more and more people are beginning to miss rural life when they were young . however , " hometown is the most beautiful place to remember , " and the brand design of " huanxiang people " is named after the hometown and hometown worries of people in wandering counties . "
circular County special climatic conditions , long sunshine time , large temperature difference day and night , characteristics of small grocery planting conditions are unique .
China is home to more than 20 kinds of small miscellaneous grains , with the highest output in Gansu and the highest quality in the country .
Wang xiaoli , a girl from huanxian county who studied in Tianjin , attended the promotion meeting as a volunteer . she said : " hometown people are the kindest and hometown people are the most beautiful . the ' huanxiang people ' brand has evoked too much homesickness , memories , and yearning for food . we hope that the ' huanxiang people ' brand will go farther and bigger . "
according to Dr. tan bin , a researcher at the scientific research institute of the state grain and material reserve bureau , through testing more than 900 sets of indicator data , agricultural products such as buckwheat , tarry buckwheat , and black beans in huanxian county have outstanding advantages in terms of testing data , and the contents of many physiological active substances in miscellaneous grain are higher than the standard data . " huanxiang people " have the inherent advantage of grabbing the high - end grocery market in china .
Qi chun , secretary of the huanxian county CPC committee , said : through the publication of the " huanxiang people 's " brand , we can further improve the quality , standardization , and scale of innovation and development of high - quality agricultural products in huanxian county . this will help shape a good overall image of agricultural products in huanxian county and rapidly raise their visibility , competitiveness , and added value .
Canada &apos;s higher @-@ than @-@ expected 0.2 per cent growth in gross domestic product ( GDP ) in July than it had been a month earlier warmed expectations that the central bank of Canada would raise interest rates next month .
if it did , it would be the fifth rate hike by the central bank in a little over a year .
analysts interviewed by Reuters had previously predicted a 0.1 per cent growth rate .
statistics Canada said Friday that 12 out of 20 industries are growing .
the figure is worth noting because the central bank predicted earlier this month that temporary factors could drag down third @-@ quarter GDP figures .
Canadian central bank chief Boroz pledged Thursday that the central bank would continue to raise interest rates gradually and would pay close attention to economic data .
the Bank of Canada &apos;s next rate decision will be announced on October 24 .
with Canada &apos;s economy strengthening and unemployment near record lows , the Central Bank of Canada has raised interest rates four times since July 2017 .
Stephen Brown , a senior Canadian economist at CIC Macro , says the country &apos;s third @-@ quarter annual GDP growth rate is expected to reach about 2 per cent .
&quot; this will be higher than the 1.5 per cent expected by the Bank of Canada and will therefore be another reason to expect a rate hike by the Bank of Canada next month , &quot; he said in a report .
the overnight index swap showed that the market forecast for the central bank of canada to raise interest rates in october rose from 76.46 percent to 78.27 percent .
South korea 's first joint inspection tour to Haikou in 65 years
South korea 's ministry of national defense confirmed on the 5 th that south korea and north korea launched a joint inspection tour into the Haikou waters of the han and linjin rivers on the same day .
the initiative is a preliminary preparation for guaranteeing the free navigation of civilian vessels on both sides .
according to a news briefing given to the media on the same day by the rok defense ministry , this was the first joint inspection of the Haikou port of the han Jiang since the signing of the Korean war armistice agreement in 1953 .
the rok and the DPRK signed a military agreement in september this year , agreeing to jointly inspect the Hanjiang estuary and other waters from november to ensure environmental protection and develop tourism in the waters in the future .
in october , the rok and the DPRK made plans for a joint inspection of the waters at the general - level meeting .
on 5 november , a joint inspection tour of the waters of the rok and the DPRK officially started .
the joint study group was composed of 20 military personnel and experts from the rok and the DPRK .
according to the rok ministry of national defense , during the inspection , the personnel of both sides did not carry weapons and prohibited the use of words and deeds to stimulate the other side .
&quot; since there was no military demarcation line near the mouth of the sea , the area used to be a high @-@ incidence area , but through joint expeditions it will be transformed into a new zone of peace in the future . &quot;
the waters jointly inspected by south korea and north korea totaled about 70 kilometers , with a total area of about 280 square kilometers .
the ministry of national defense said that the rok will send six research boats to explore the depth of the sea to provide basic information for the safe navigation of the waters , and will provide navigational maps for the movement of civilian vessels after the survey is completed .
South Korea and the Democratic People &apos;s Republic of Korea held a summit meeting in Pyongyang in October 2007 to reach an agreement on the joint use of the Han and Linjin rivers at the mouth of the sea , but subsequent talks were stalled because of tensions on the peninsula .
according to a military agreement signed by south korea and north korea in september , vessels from both sides will need to inform each other in advance before sailing in common waters in the future .
chinanews , Nov. 5 - chinese citizens Guo yuqin and Mao ronxin lost links during their trip to mongolia , according to the website of the chinese embassy in mongolia on november 4 .
it was learned that the two men were members of the blue sky rescue team . on 19 october , the two men contacted relatives and friends in the country , saying that they would soon explore the mountains near lake kuskur and share their positions through micromail . they have since lost contact and are suspected to have gone to no one 's land .
the Chinese Embassy in Mongolia has always attached great importance to the protection of the legitimate rights and security of Chinese citizens in Mongolia and to consular protection and assistance .
upon learning of the loss of the two tourists mentioned above , the embassy immediately started to receive emergency plans to seize the golden rescue time and make every effort to carry out its work .
the Embassy maintained close communication with the families of the persons concerned , assisted them in reporting the cases immediately to the Mongolian police , and provided them with a list of interpreters to choose from .
the embassy immediately met with the responsible persons of the Mongolian Ministry of External Relations , the General Police Department and the General Emergency Department to brief them on the situation , and asked the Mongolian side to conduct a search and rescue operation as soon as possible , and to maintain close communication with the Mongolian side throughout the search and rescue process to ensure that the latest progress is kept abreast of in a timely manner .
at the same time , the embassy assisted families in mongolia in publicizing the search notices , extensively mobilized overseas chinese in mongolia and chinese - funded enterprises to actively participate in the search , provided effective clues , and provided relevant assistance to a number of blue sky rescue team members who went to mongolia to assist in the rescue .
under the strong impetus of the embassy , the Mongolian side dispatched rescue teams as soon as possible and promised to waive the search and rescue fees .
the Mongol Police Directorate and the Emergency Department instructed the police and the Emergency Department of the province of Kousugur to conduct a full search and rescue operation .
due to the fact that Lake Kusuguru is located in the northern part of Mongolia at the border with Russia . it is located in a remote and sparsely populated area . transportation and communications are extremely difficult . at present , Mongolia has entered a severe winter with temperatures as low as about 20 degrees below zero . local police and emergency departments have overcome enormous difficulties and mobilized almost all police forces . they have also mobilized local herdsmen to carry out a wide range of ground search and rescue operations around the disconnected location of the two men for several days .
at the same time , in response to the special situation of the pastoral areas , the Mongol side has been broadcasting circular notices for many days .
domestic Blue Sky Rescue Team has also come to Mongolia to participate actively in the rescue .
the safety of the two disconnected personnel has always struck our hearts .
it has been more than 10 days since the two men lost their connection , and the embassy has successively received some clues , but they have not yet been located . at present , the search and rescue operation is still going on intensively .
in keeping with the principle of " putting people first , " the embassy will continue to pay attention to this matter , urge the Mongolian side to continue to make full efforts to search and rescue , and provide maximum assistance to the families of the people concerned .
the embassy calls on compatriots and enterprises in mongolia to contact the chinese embassy in mongolia as soon as possible if they have relevant clues .
